at%20achievement%2C%20combined%20with%20the%20English%20Channel%20(20.5%20miles)%20and%20Catalina%20channel%20(20%20miles)%20swims%2C%20earned%20him%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flongswims.com%2Fp%2Fed-horne%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETriple%20Crown%20of%20Open%20Water%20Swimming%20status%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20mark%20recognized%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguinness-world-records-surviving-age-of-internet-and-social-media-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGuinness%20World%20Records%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHorne%20is%20the%20oldest%20person%20to%20conquer%20all%203%20swims%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20been%20only%20drizzling%20when%20the%20Manhattan%20adventure%20got%20underway.%20Nathaniel%20Johnston%2C%20a%20kayaker%2C%20was%20tucked%20under%20the%20spray%20skirt%20of%20his%20craft.%20Captain%20Thomas%20Crystall%20took%20the%20helm%20of%20a%20small%20rigid-hull%20inflatable%20boat.%20An%20official%20observer%2C%20Louise%20Darlington%2C%20was%20on%20deck%20to%20ensure%20swimmer%20safety%20and%20adherence%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarathonswimmers.org%2Frules%2F6_observers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Erules%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20chiefly%2C%20not%20touching%20the%20kayak%20or%20other%20people%2C%20which%20could%20be%20construed%20as%20an%20assist%20and%20disqualify%20the%20swim%20from%20formal%20recognition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20crew%20set%20to%20strategize%20the%20best%20timing%20for%20getting%20around%20the%20massive%20Staten%20Island%20Ferry.%20Horne%20took%20his%20first%20strokes%20with%20the%20Statue%20of%20Liberty%20in%20sight.%20By%20the%20time%20they%20got%20to%20the%20Brooklyn%20Bridge%2C%20it%20was%20pouring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWow%2C%20this%20is%20really%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnston%20said%2C%20recalling%20his%20thoughts%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BThe%20wind%20is%20blowing%20in%20my%20face.%20I%20couldn't%20see%20more%20than%2050%20yards%20ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221728%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Man%20swimming%20past%20the%20statue%20of%20liberty%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564b7f3c58b6f84123a615d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221296%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHorne%20and%20his%20crew%20with%20the%20Statue%20of%20Liberty%20in%20sight.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Horne's%20dedicated%20kayaker%2C%20Johnston%20was%20tasked%20with%20passing%20%26quot%3Bfeeds%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20swimmer%3A%20carbohydrate%20powder%20in%20water%20with%20concentrated%20fruit%20juice%2C%20electrolytes%2C%20bananas%2C%20and%20peaches%20%E2%80%94%20plus%20an%20occasional%20caffeine%20pill%20for%20a%20man%20accustomed%20to%20two%20cappuccinos%20and%20a%20double%20espresso%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDarlington%20monitored%20adherence%20to%20protocol%20from%20a%20vantage%20that%20offered%20little%20protection%20from%20heavy%20horizontal%20rain.%20Her%20logs%20would%20be%20necessary%20to%20ensure%20ratification%20of%20the%20swim.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%20getting%20hammered%2C%20but%20she%20did%20a%20wonderful%2C%20wonderful%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Horne%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDarlington%20had%20taken%20on%20the%20role%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20when%20the%20scheduled%20observer%20missed%20the%20start%20time%2C%20having%20confused%20it%20with%20a%20second%20swim%20he%20was%20scheduled%20to%20monitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHorne%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flongswims.com%2Finsights%2Ftriple-crown%2F%23oldest%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoldest%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20finish%20the%20three%20swims%20at%2067.8%20years%20old.%20He%20pushed%20American%20Eric%20Durban%20to%20second%20place%20since%20he%20was%20only%2067%20years%20old%20when%20he%20finished%20the%20same%20swims.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20state%20of%20emergency%20was%20declared%20while%20he%20swam%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20hours%2C%20Horne%20dodged%20plastic%2C%20tissues%2C%20and%20leaves%20%E2%80%94%20the%20usual%20assortment%20expected%20in%20Big%20Apple%20waterways%20with%20a%20huge%20rainfall.%20Navigating%20his%20way%20toward%20the%20Triborough%20Bridge%2C%20the%20British%20mergers-and-acquisitions%20specialist%20had%20no%20clue%20that%20the%20New%20York%20City%20governor%20had%20declared%20a%20state%20of%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20wasn't%20Horne's%20first%20brush%20with%20savage%20weather.%20He%20was%20forced%20to%20call%20it%20quits%20during%20a%20%26quot%3B20%20Bridges%26quot%3B%20try%20in%20July%20when%20lightning%20lit%20up%20the%20river%20beneath%20him%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20happened%20at%20the%2019th%20bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20heartbreaking%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnston%20said%2C%20was%20that%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20we%20got%20on%20land%2C%20the%20storm%20went%20away.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20all%20just%20sitting%20there%20at%20night%20on%20this%20pier%2C%20watching%20it%20suddenly%20clear%20up%20and%20turning%20into%20a%20beautiful%20evening.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHe's%20not%20one%20to%20give%20up%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Horne%20is%20not%20one%20to%20give%20up%3A%20It%20took%20him%20three%20tries%20to%20cross%20the%20English%20Channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20first%20try%2C%20in%202020%2C%20he%20swam%20in%20brutal%20waters.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20you%20would%20breathe%2C%20you%20didn't%20know%20whether%20you%20were%20getting%20air%20or%20water%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20seemed%20to%20be%20bouncing%20around%20like%20a%20washing%20machine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExcruciating%20cramps%20took%20him%20out%20in%202021.%20Finally%2C%20in%202022%2C%20he%20reached%20the%20seaside%20town%20of%20Wissant%2C%20France%20%E2%80%94%20in%2015%20hours%20and%2051%20minutes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20English%20Channel%20under%20his%20belt%20and%20one%20aborted%20attempt%20at%20%26quot%3B20%20Bridges%2C%26quot%3B%20Horne%20set%20his%20sights%20in%20August%20on%20California's%20Catalina%20channel.%20It%20shook%20him%20to%20the%20core.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20the%20darkest%20night%20I%20have%20ever%20done%2C%20there%20were%20no%20stars.%20There%20were%20no%20other%20boats%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kayaker%20who%20followed%20him%20attached%20glow%20sticks%20to%20the%20feeds.%20Through%20steamy%20goggles%2C%20Horne%20pushed%20on%20for%20seven%20hours%20as%20darkness%20ate%20into%20his%20psyche.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20finished%20Catalina%20in%2013%20hours%20and%2043%20minutes%20and%20was%20determined%20to%20get%20back%20to%20the%20Big%20Apple%20for%20that%20elusive%2020th%20bridge%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20Triple%20Crown.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20him%2C%20victory%20was%20sweet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20George%20Washington%20Bridge%20now%20will%20always%20have%20a%20place%20in%20my%20heart%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20NYC's%20Pier%20A%20at%20the%20finish%2C%20Horne%20messaged%20a%20local%20swim%20group%20that%20had%20been%20tracking%20his%20swim%20by%20app%20and%20eagerly%20awaiting%20news%3A%20%26quot%3BCompleted%20the%2020%20Bridges%20in%20the%20most%20diabolical%20weather%20and%20was%20greeted%20by%20one%20total%20stranger%20who%20turned%20his%20back%20on%20us!!%26quot%3B%20His%20tone%20was%20jovial.%20He%20praised%20his%20crew%2C%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BStrong%20winds%20and%20horizontal%20rain.%20It%20was%20slightly%20more%20fun%20in%20the%20water!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F20-bridges-swim-record-tropical-storm-ophelia-2023-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701109556000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6564b781fd6200867dcf9fb7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F