m%2Fmajedalansari%2Fstatus%2F1729171016642166998%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2027%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHamas%2C%20which%20runs%20Gaza%20and%20triggered%20the%20latest%20round%20of%20fighting%20by%20launching%20a%20bloody%20cross-border%20raid%20last%20month%2C%20said%20it%20was%20drawing%20up%20a%20new%20list%20of%20hostages%20for%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20office%20of%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20said%20it%20had%20informed%20families%20of%20the%20identities%20of%20hostages%20to%20be%20released%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20last%20day%20of%20the%20initial%20four-day%20truce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20been%20clear%20that%20the%20pause%20is%20designed%20to%20allow%20Hamas%20to%20free%20more%20of%20the%20hostages%20it%20is%20holding%20since%20the%20October%207%20attack%2C%20which%20killed%201%2C200%20Israelis%20including%20many%20women%20and%20children%2C%20according%20to%20Israeli%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20both%20sides%20are%20under%20pressure%20to%20build%20on%20the%20break%20in%20hostilities%20to%20allow%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20reach%20civilians%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20Israel's%20campaign%20against%20Hamas%20has%20left%20almost%2015%2C000%20dead%2C%20mostly%20Palestinian%20civilians%2C%20according%20to%20Gaza's%20Hamas%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Qatari%20announcement%20came%20after%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20top%20EU%20envoy%20Josep%20Borrell%20and%20NATO%20Secretary%20General%20Jens%20Stoltenberg%20all%20joined%20a%20global%20chorus%20urging%20the%20parties%20to%20extend%20their%20temporary%20break%20in%20fighting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20truce%20deal%2C%20Hamas%20has%20so%20far%20released%2039%20Israeli%20hostages%2C%20including%20a%20four-year-old%20girl%20orphaned%20by%20the%20group's%20October%207%20attack%2C%20with%20more%20expected%20later%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPublic%20health%20'catastrophe'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20freed%20117%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20under%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20agreement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20parallel%2C%2019%20foreign%20nationals%20have%20also%20been%20released%20by%20Palestinian%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETearful%20reunions%20of%20families%20and%20hostages%20have%20brought%20relief%20from%20images%20of%20civilian%20death%20and%20suffering%20in%20the%20seven-week%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20our%20goal%2C%20to%20keep%20this%20pause%20going%20beyond%20tomorrow%20so%20that%20we%20can%20continue%20to%20see%20more%20hostages%20come%20out%20and%20surge%20more%20humanitarian%20relief%20in%20to%20those%20in%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20Biden%20said%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20welcomed%20the%20agreement%20to%20extend%20the%20truce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20would%20of%20course%20hope%20to%20see%20the%20pause%20extended%20further%2C%20and%20that%20will%20depend%20upon%20Hamas%20continuing%20to%20release%20hostages%2C%26quot%3B%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKirby%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bin%20order%20to%20extend%20the%20pause%2C%20Hamas%20has%20committed%20to%20releasing%20another%2020%20women%20and%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EU's%20Borrell%20had%20called%20for%20the%20pause%20to%20be%20prolonged%20%26quot%3Bto%20make%20it%20sustainable%20and%20long%20lasting%20while%20working%20for%20a%20political%20solution.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20can%20justify%20the%20indiscriminate%20brutality%20Hamas%20unleashed%20against%20civilians%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20one%20horror%20cannot%20justify%20another%20horror.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20successive%20days%20of%20hostage%20releases%20have%20buoyed%20spirits%20in%20Israel%2C%20with%20tearful%20reunions%20weeks%20after%20Hamas%20militants%20poured%20across%20the%20border%20on%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20group%20of%20hostages%20released%20Sunday%20included%20a%20four-year-old%20American%20citizen%20called%20Abigail%20whose%20parents%20were%20both%20killed%20in%20the%20Hamas%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInside%20Gaza%2C%20the%20Hamas-run%20health%20ministry%20complained%20that%2C%20despite%20the%20four-day%20pause%2C%20no%20fuel%20had%20been%20taken%20to%20generators%20in%20hospitals%20in%20the%20north%20of%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20Yahya%20al-Siraj%2C%20the%20mayor%20of%20Gaza%20City%2C%20complained%20that%20without%20fuel%20the%20territory%20could%20not%20pump%20clean%20water%20nor%20clear%20waste%20accumulating%20in%20the%20streets%2C%20warning%20of%20a%20potential%20public%20health%20%26quot%3Bcatastrophe%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20French%20warship%20arrived%20in%20the%20Egyptian%20town%20of%20El-Arish%20near%20the%20border%20with%20Gaza%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20hospital%20for%20wounded%20civilians%2C%20a%20port%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EFight%20'until%20victory'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20faced%20mounting%20pressure%20to%20extend%20the%20pause%20mediated%20by%20Qatar%2C%20the%20United%20States%20and%20Egypt%2C%20though%20its%20leaders%20have%20dismissed%20any%20suggestions%20of%20a%20lasting%20halt%20to%20the%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20until%20the%20end%20--%20until%20victory%2C%26quot%3B%20Netanyahu%20said%20in%20Gaza%20on%20Sunday%2C%20on%20the%20first%20visit%20by%20an%20Israeli%20premier%20since%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20office%20has%20proposed%20a%20war%20budget%20of%2030%20billion%20shekels%20(%248%20billion)%20for%2090%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWearing%20military%20fatigues%20and%20surrounded%20by%20soldiers%2C%20Netanyahu%20vowed%20to%20free%20all%20the%20hostages%20and%20%26quot%3Beliminate%20Hamas%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20footage%20posted%20online%20by%20his%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20sign%20of%20mounting%20international%20concern%2C%20UN%20rights%20experts%20called%20Monday%20for%20independent%20investigations%20into%20alleged%20war%20crimes%20and%20crimes%20against%20humanity%20carried%20out%20in%20Israel%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20territories%20since%20October%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMorris%20Tidball-Binz%2C%20the%20United%20Nations%20special%20rapporteur%20on%20extrajudicial%20executions%2C%20and%20Alice%20Jill%20Edwards%2C%20the%20special%20rapporteur%20on%20torture%2C%20issued%20a%20joint%20statement%20stressing%20the%20need%20for%20%26quot%3Bprompt%2C%20transparent%20and%20independent%20investigations%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701108900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fpj691no_israel-hostage_625x300_24_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-truce-in-gaza-extended-by-2-days-mediator-qatar-4611504%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20truce%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20will%20be%20extended%20by%20two%20days%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20group%20and%20mediator%20Qatar%20said%20Monday%2C%20opening%20the%20way%20for%20further%20releases%20of%20hostages%20and%20prisoners.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-truce-in-gaza-extended-by-2-days-mediator-qatar-4611504%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-truce-in-gaza-extended-by-2-days-mediator-qatar-4611504%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-truce-in-gaza-extended-by-2-days-mediator-qatar-4611504%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%