%3A%22The%20shekel%20rose%208.8%25%20from%20a%2011-year%20low%20last%20month%2C%20as%20short%20sellers%20left%20and%20the%20Bank%20of%20Israel%20sold%20of%20billions%20of%20its%20reserves.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22fdemott%40insider.com%20(Filip%20De%20Mott)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A41%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fisrael-shekel-world-best-performing-currency-us-dollar-hamas-war-2023-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BRespiratory%20Illness%20In%20China%20Due%20To%20Common%20Viruses%26quot%3B%3A%20AIIMS%20Doctor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20rising%20cases%20of%20respiratory%20illness%20in%20China%2C%20a%20senior%20doctor%20from%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20has%20said%20that%20viral%20infections%20are%20common%20in%20winter%20and%20there%20is%20no%20possibility%20of%20another%20pandemic%20like%20Covid%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20notable%20surge%20has%20been%20reported%20in%20respiratory%20illness%20in%20children%20in%20northern%20China%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20SK%20Kabra%2C%20Head%20of%20Department%2C%20Mother%20and%20Child%20Block%2C%20AIIMS%2C%20told%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20reports%20coming%20from%20China%20now%20show%20that%20there%20has%20been%20a%20sudden%20increase%20in%20respiratory%20infections%20between%20October%20and%20November%20and%20they%20have%20observed%20that%20it%20is%20more%20common%20in%20children.%20Mycoplasma%20has%20been%20seen.%20They%20have%20not%20seen%20any%20new%20or%20unusual%20viruses.%20There%20is%20no%20indication%20yet%20that%20this%20is%20a%20new%20organism%20and%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20say%20whether%20it%20can%20cause%20a%20pandemic%20like%20Covid.%20This%20possibility%20is%20not%20there%20yet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20common%20viruses%20in%20the%20winter%20season%20have%20been%20seen%20in%20the%20reports%20coming%20from%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20experts%20have%20discussed%20this%20and%2C%20according%20to%20them%2C%20there%20could%20be%202-3%20things%20due%20to%20which%20it%20has%20increased.%20Firstly%2C%20virus%20infection%20is%20more%20common%20in%20winter%20and%20the%20main%20ones%20are%20influenza%2C%20adenovirus%20and%20mycoplasma.%20Till%20now%2C%20the%20same%20viruses%20are%20visible%20in%20the%20reports%20of%20the%20organisms%20spreading%20in%20China%20and%20there%20is%20nothing%20new.%20People%20are%20very%20worried%20because%20the%20pandemic%20has%20just%20passed%20whether%20a%20new%20virus%20has%20arrived%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Kabra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kabra%20also%20said%20that%20cases%20of%20respiratory%20illness%20may%20be%20increasing%20in%20China%20because%20of%20the%20strict%20lockdown%20which%20had%20been%20imposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSee%2C%20the%20lockdown%20in%20China%20was%20very%20strict.%20It%20was%20lifted%20in%20December%20last%20year%20and%2C%20since%20then%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20winter%20there.%20As%20far%20as%20we%20know%20about%20infection%20in%20children%2C%20every%20child%20under%205%20years%20of%20age%20gets%20a%20viral%20infection%203-8%20times%20a%20year%20and%20with%20each%20infection%2C%20he%20becomes%20immune%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20after%20the%20age%20of%205%2C%20the%20rate%20of%20infection%20reduces.%20So%20the%20children%20in%20China%20who%20are%20not%20able%20to%20come%20out%20of%20their%20houses%20due%20to%20lockdown%2C%20their%20immunity%20has%20not%20developed%20due%20to%20which%20they%20have%20become%20susceptible%20to%20the%20infection%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20hypothesis%20that%20the%20children%20who%20have%20not%20had%20this%20infection%20in%202-3%20years%20during%20lockdown%2C%20the%20infection%20will%20now%20occur.%20If%20one%20child%20gets%20it%2C%20it%20will%20infect%2010%20more%2C%20due%20to%20which%20the%20cases%20will%20increase%20suddenly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20people%20to%20practice%20hygiene%20and%20use%20sanitisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20child%20has%20an%20infection%2C%20do%20not%20send%20him%20outside%20until%20he%20recovers.%20Generally%2C%20influenza%20lasts%20for%20a%20week.%20One%20can%20use%20a%20mask%20and%20follow%20social%20distancing.%20Everyone%20should%20also%20take%20care%20of%20hygiene%2C%20and%20use%20sanitisers.%20The%20phase%20that%20China%20is%20facing%20now%2C%20we%20have%20already%20faced%20it%20last%20year%2C%20so%20there%20is%20no%20problem%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20doctor%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20now%20more%20knowledgeable%20than%20before%20about%20how%20a%20pandemic%20is%20managed.%20The%20ministry%20has%20told%20doctors%20to%20investigate%20if%20such%20cases%20are%20coming.%20If%20any%20abnormality%20is%20seen%2C%20then%20inform%20them%20so%20that%20appropriate%20action%20can%20be%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701102600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fe8ul6shg_china-reuters_625x300_23_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frespiratory-illness-in-china-due-to-common-viruses-aiims-doctor-4611531%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20rising%20cases%20of%20respiratory%20illness%20in%20China%2C%20a%20senior%20doctor%20from%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20has%20said%20that%20viral%20infections%20are%20common%20in%20winter%20and%20there%20is%20no%20possibility%20of%20another%20pandemic%20like%20Covid%20yet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frespi