%20is%20determining%20if%20armed%20attacks%20on%20the%20capital%2C%20Freetown%2C%20were%20an%20attempted%20coup.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A43%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67541728%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67541728.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67541728.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel's%20Netanyahu%20Shows%20Elon%20Musk%20Footage%20Of%20October%207%20Hamas%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETech%20entrepreneur%20Elon%20Musk%20lent%20support%20on%20Monday%20to%20Israel's%20campaign%20against%20Hamas%2C%20saying%20one%20challenge%20was%20stopping%20propaganda%20of%20a%20sort%20that%20led%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20faction's%20killing%20spree%20that%20triggered%20the%20Gaza%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20owner%20of%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20X%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%2C%20Musk%20was%20on%20an%20unusual%20visit%20to%20Israel%2C%20during%20a%20four-day%20pause%20to%20the%20fighting%2C%20and%20held%20a%20live%20online%20discussion%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20Netanyahu%20describe%20the%20destruction%20of%20Hamas%2C%20which%20Israel%20has%20set%20as%20a%20war%20goal%2C%20as%20necessary%20for%20any%20prospective%20peace%20with%20the%20Palestinians%2C%20Musk%20sounded%20his%20general%20agreement%20for%20such%20objectives%20during%20an%20X%20Spaces%20discussion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Musk%2C%20who%20also%20owns%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BI'd%20like%20to%20help%20as%20well.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20that%20are%20intent%20on%20murder%20must%20be%20neutralised%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20propaganda%20must%20stop%20that%20is%20training%20people%20to%20be%20murderers%20in%20the%20future.%20And%20then%2C%20making%20Gaza%20prosperous.%20And%20if%20that%20happens%2C%20I%20think%20it%20will%20be%20a%20good%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20you%20will%20be%20involved.%20And%20the%20fact%20that%20you%20came%20here%2C%20I%20think%2C%20speaks%20volumes%20to%20your%20commitment%20to%20try%20to%20secure%20a%20better%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20has%20himself%20been%20accused%20of%20incitement%20after%20agreeing%20on%20November%2015%20with%20a%20post%20that%20falsely%20claimed%20Jews%20were%20stoking%20hatred%20against%20white%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20showed%20Musk%20some%20footage%20of%20the%20Oct.%207%20attack%20assembled%20from%20Hamas%20bodycams%2C%20CCTV%20and%20other%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20they%20last%20met%2C%20in%20California%20on%20Sept.%2018%2C%20Netanyahu%20urged%20Musk%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20protecting%20free%20expression%20and%20fighting%20hate%20speech%20after%20weeks%20of%20controversy%20over%20antisemitism%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk%20said%20previously%20that%20he%20opposed%20anything%20that%20%26quot%3Bpromotes%20hate%20and%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20any%20X%20content.%20In%20a%20possible%20reference%20to%20his%20solidarity%20visit%20to%20Israel%2C%20Musk%20posted%20on%20X%20earlier%20on%20Monday%3A%20%26quot%3BActions%20speak%20louder%20than%20words.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20due%20to%20meet%20Israeli%20President%20Isaac%20Herzog%20and%20families%20of%20hostages%20held%20by%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza.%20Herzog's%20office%20said%20he%20and%20Musk%20would%20discuss%20%26quot%3Bthe%20need%20to%20act%20to%20combat%20rising%20antisemitism%20online%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20as%20the%20war%20raged%2C%20Musk%20proposed%20using%20Starlink%20to%20support%20communication%20links%20in%20the%20blackout-hit%20Gaza%20enclave%20with%20%26quot%3Binternationally%20recognised%20aid%20organizations%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Israeli%20Communications%20Minister%20Shlomo%20Karhi%20objected%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3BHamas%20will%20use%20it%20(Starlink)%20for%20terrorist%20activities%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20a%20new%20tack%20on%20Monday%2C%20Karhi%20said%20Israel%20and%20Musk%20had%20reached%20an%20agreement%20in%20principle%20whereby%20%26quot%3BStarlink%20satellite%20units%20can%20only%20be%20operated%20in%20Israel%20with%20the%20approval%20of%20the%20Israeli%20Ministry%20of%20Communications%2C%20including%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20X%20post%20addressed%20to%20Musk%2C%20Karhi%20said%20he%20hoped%20the%20visit%20to%20Israel%20%26quot%3Bwill%20serve%20as%20a%20springboard%20for%20future%20endeavours%2C%20as%20well%20as%20enhance%20your%20relationship%20with%20the%20Jewish%20people%20and%20values%20we%20share%20with%20the%20entire%20world%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20Nov.%2015%20comment%20on%20X%2C%20Musk%20added%20the%20view%20that%20the%20user%20who%20referenced%20the%20false%20%26quot%3BGreat%20Replacement%26quot%3B%20conspiracy%20theory%20was%20speaking%20%26quot%3Bthe%20actual%20truth%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20theory%20holds%20that%20Jewish%20people%20and%20leftists%20are%20engineering%20the%20ethnic%20and%20cultural%20replacement%20of%20white%20populations%20with%20non-white%20immigrants%20that%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bwhite%20genocide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20that%20comment%2C%20the%20White%20House%20condemned%20what%20it%20called%20an%20%26quot%3Babhorrent%20promotion%20of%20antisemitic%20and%20racist%20hate%26quot%3B%20that%20%26quot%3Bruns%20against%20our%20core%20values%20as%20Americans%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20U.S.%20companies%20including%20Walt%20Disney%2C%20Warner%20Bros%20Discovery%20and%20NBCUniversal%20parent%20Comcast%20paused%20their%20advertisements%20on%20his%20social%20media%20s