ikas%20Nigam%20Limited%20(RVNL)%20and%20Satlej%20Jal%20Vidyut%20Nigam%20Limited%20and%20also%20examined%20the%20work%20on%20the%20170-metre%20perpendicular%20tunnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mishra%20interacted%20with%20the%20trapped%20workers%20through%20the%20communication%20line%20and%20assured%20them%20of%20their%20safe%20rescue.%20Sources%20said%20the%20workers%20exuded%20confidence%20and%20optimism.%20He%20also%20spoke%20to%20the%20family%20members%20of%20the%20labourers%20and%20gave%20them%20the%20same%20assurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20principal%20secretary%20advised%20the%20agencies%20to%20conduct%20the%20rescue%20operation%20at%20a%20fast%20pace%20while%20prioritising%20the%20safety%20of%20men%20and%20machinery.%20He%20also%20instructed%20them%20to%20ensure%20the%20well-being%20of%20the%20trapped%20workers%20with%20a%20timely%20supply%20of%20food%20and%20other%20daily-use%20items.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Mishra%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20continuous%20health%20monitoring%20of%20the%20trapped%20workers%20and%20said%20there%20should%20be%20periodic%20counselling%20sessions%20for%20their%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20principal%20secretary%20appreciated%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20various%20ground%20staff%20like%20machine%20operators%2C%20welders%2C%20rat%20miners%2C%20police%2C%20national%20and%20state%20disaster%20response%20forces%2C%20Border%20Roads%20Organisation%2C%20Army%2C%20Indo%20Tibetan%20Border%20Police%2C%20district%20administration%20and%20all%20the%20other%20agencies%20involved%20in%20the%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20teams%20began%20manual%20drilling%20at%20the%20site%20on%20Monday%20evening%20and%20another%20pipe%20has%20been%20pushed%20in%20about%20one%20metre%20ahead%20of%20the%20place%20where%20the%20auger%20machine%20had%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20under-construction%20Silkyara-Dandalgaon%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarkashi%20is%20part%20of%20the%20ambitious%20Char%20Dham%20project%20to%20enhance%20connectivity%20to%20the%20Hindu%20pilgrimage%20sites%20of%20Badrinath%2C%20Kedarnath%2C%20Gangotri%2C%20and%20Yamunotri.%20The%20workers%20got%20trapped%20when%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20tunnel%20collapsed%20on%20November%2012%2C%20the%20day%20of%20Diwali.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701098700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F9a9u3vg_pk-mishra-uttarakhand-tunnel_625x300_27_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarakhand-tunnel-rescue-will-get-you-out-safely-pms-principal-secretary-tells-workers-trapped-in-tunnel-4611311%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20the%2016th%20day%20of%20the%20operation%20to%20rescue%2041%20labourers%20trapped%20in%20a%20tunnel%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Principal%20Secretary%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20PK%20Mishra%2C%20visited%20the%20site%20and%20assured%20the%20teams%20of%20all%20possible%20support%20from%20the%20Union%20government.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarakhand-tunnel-rescue-will-get-you-out-safely-pms-principal-secretary-tells-workers-trapped-in-tunnel-4611311%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarakhand-tunnel-rescue-will-get-you-out-safely-pms-principal-secretary-tells-workers-trapped-in-tunnel-4611311%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-tunnel-uttarakhand-tunnel-rescue-will-get-you-out-safely-pms-principal-secretary-tells-workers-trapped-in-tunnel-4611311%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Drilling%20Down%20Uttarakhand%20Tunnel%20Makes%20Progress%3B%20%E2%80%98Rat%20Miners%E2%80%99%20Reportedly%20Begin%20Work%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2