20Manual%20Drilling%20At%20Uttarakhand%20Tunnel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EManual%20horizontal%20drilling%20has%20started%20at%20the%20Uttarakhand%20tunnel%20where%2041%20men%20have%20been%20trapped%20for%20more%20than%20two%20weeks%2C%20the%20authorities%20have%20said.%20The%20process%20started%20at%207%20this%20evening%20after%20the%20American%20Augur%20Drill%20broke%20again%2C%20its%20blades%20fouled%20up%20by%20iron%20grill%20from%20the%20tunnel%20ceiling%20and%20other%20debris.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20work%20is%20being%20conducted%20by%20%26quot%3Brat%20miners%26quot%3B%E2%80%94labourers%20used%20to%20drilling%20narrow%20shafts%20as%20part%20of%20a%20primitive%20method%20of%20coal%20extraction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vertical%20drilling%20to%20create%20an%20extra%20passageway%20has%20already%20progressed%20to%2036%20meters%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManual%20drilling%20from%20top%20and%20side%20are%20the%20two%20methods%20on%20which%20rescue%20workers%20are%20focussing%20on%20after%20several%20other%20methods%20failed.%20Horizontal%20drilling%20from%20the%20Barkot%20end%20of%20the%20tunnel%20is%20also%20in%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeraj%20Khairwal%2C%20Secretary%2C%20Uttarakhand%20government%2C%20said%2024%20rat%20miners%20will%20work%2024%20hours%20to%20remove%20manual%20debris.%20The%20work%20will%20be%20done%20in%20three%20shifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Auger%20Machine%2C%20once%20in%20working%20condition%2C%20will%20push%20the%20800-mm%20pipe%20forward%20as%20the%20manual%20drilling%20progresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%2C%20however%2C%20refused%20to%20give%20a%20time%20frame%20for%20the%20rescue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManual%20drilling%20is%20a%20slow%20and%20labour-intensive%20process%20in%20which%20the%20rat-hole%20miners%20will%20go%20through%20the%20800%20mm%20pipe%2C%20drill%20manually%20and%20bring%20out%20the%20debris%20by%20shovels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20going%20through%20the%20800-mm%20diame