l%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105539379%2Cimgsize-28474.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fhardik-pandya-pens-heartfelt-note-for-gujarat-titans-as-he-leaves-for-mumbai-indians%2Farticleshow%2F105539154.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Star%20all-rounder%20Hardik%20Pandya%20made%20a%20notable%20return%20to%20his%20former%20team%2C%20the%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20in%20an%20all-cash%20trade-off%20with%20the%20Gujarat%20Titans.%20During%20his%20tenure%2C%20Pandya%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20guiding%20the%20team%20to%20victory%20in%20their%20debut%20season%20in%202022%2C%20featuring%20in%2031%20matches.%20He%20showcased%20his%20batting%20prowess%2C%20accumulating%20833%20runs%20at%20an%20impressive%20average%20of%2037.86%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20exceeding%20133.%20With%20six%20half-centuries%20and%20a%20top%20score%20of%2087*%2C%20his%20contribution%20was%20significant.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Are%20India%20%26quot%3BSerious%20Challengers%26quot%3B%20For%202024%20T20%20WC%3F%20Shastri's%20Blunt%20Verdict%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20head%20coach%20Ravi%20Shastri%20on%20Monday%20backed%20India%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%20challengers%26quot%3B%20in%20next%20year's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20but%20said%20what%20matters%20for%20a%20dominant%20side%20is%20to%20come%20out%20winners%20in%20the%20last%20two%20knock-out%20games%20of%20any%20big%20event.%20It%20has%20been%20more%20than%20a%20week%20since%20Australia%20trumped%20India%2C%20in%20what%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20one-sided%20final%20in%20Ahmedabad%2C%20with%20the%20country's%20cricket%20fraternity%20still%20reeling%20with%20the%20outcome%2C%20given%20that%20the%20hosts%20had%20a%2010-match%20unbeaten%20run%20into%20the%20title%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3