cket%2C%20the%20very%20next%20one%20India%20will%20be%20very%20serious%20challengers%20because%20you%20have%20got%20the%20nucleus%2C%20this%20is%20a%20shorter%20format%20of%20the%20game.%20Your%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20that.%26quot%3B%20Shastri%20admitted%20that%20it%20still%20hurts%20to%20recall%20that%20India%2C%20who%20were%20the%20strongest%20team%20in%20the%20competition%2C%20did%20not%20deliver%20in%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20fabulous%2C%26quot%3B%20Shastri%20said%2C%20recalling%20India's%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20honest%2C%20it%20still%20hurts%20from%20the%20outside%2C%20that%20we%20could%20not%20win%20the%20cup%20because%20we%20were%20the%20strongest%20team.%26quot%3B%20With%20the%20Indian%20bowlers%20performing%20in%20unison%20led%20by%20Mohammed%20Shami%2C%20who%20claimed%2024%20wickets%2C%20Shastri%20said%20it%20gave%20India%20the%20'best%20chance'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20way%20the%20bowling%20stood%20up%20towards%20the%20mid%20stage%20of%20the%20tournament%20you%20thought%20they%20had%20a%20great%2C%20great%20chance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701096660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-05%2F725jcqgo_ravi-shastri-happy-bcciipl_625x300_29_May_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fare-india-serious-challengers-for-2024-t20-world-cup-ravi-shastris-blunt-verdict-4609673%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20has%20been%20more%20than%20a%20week%20since%20Australia%20trumped%20India%2C%20in%20what%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20one-sided%20final%20in%20Ahmedabad%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fare-india-serious-challengers-for-2024-t20-world-cup-ravi-shastris-blunt-verdic