pUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Confirms%20First%20Human%20Case%20Of%20Swine%20Flu%20Strain%20H1N2%3A%20Health%20Agency%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUK%20public%20health%20officials%20on%20Monday%20said%20they%20had%20confirmed%20a%20first%20human%20case%20of%20a%20swine%20flu%20strain%20similar%20to%20one%20that%20has%20been%20circulating%20in%20pigs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20variant%20of%20the%20H1N2%20virus%20was%20confirmed%20in%20an%20individual%20who%20had%20been%20tested%20by%20their%20doctor%20after%20experiencing%20respiratory%20symptoms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20not%20previously%20been%20detected%20in%20humans%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20UK%20Health%20Security%20Agency%20(UKHSA)%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20we%20have%20detected%20this%20virus%20in%20humans%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20though%20it%20is%20very%20similar%20to%20viruses%20that%20have%20been%20detected%20in%20pigs%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20agency's%20incident%20director%20Meera%20Chand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20working%20rapidly%20to%20trace%20close%20contacts%20and%20reduce%20any%20potential%20spread.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20individual%20concerned%20experienced%20a%20mild%20illness%20and%20had%20fully%20recovered%2C%20the%20agency%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20of%20their%20infection%2C%20however%2C%20was%20undetermined%20and%20is%20being%20investigated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUKHSA%20chief%20veterinary%20officer%20Christine%20Middlemiss%20said%20veterinary%20and%20scientific%20knowledge%20is%20being%20provided%20to%20support%20its%20probe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInfluenza%20A(H1)%20viruses%20are%20endemic%20in%20swine%20populations%20in%20most%20regions%20of%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20H1N1%2C%20H1N2%20and%20H3N2%20viruses%20are%20major%20subtypes%20of%20swine%20influenza%20A%20viruses%20in%20pigs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20occasionally%20infect%20humans%2C%20usually%20after%20direct%20or%20indirect%20exposure%20to%20pigs%20or%20contaminated%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20H1N1%20pandemic%20in%202009%20was%20the%20first%20major%20influenza%20outbreak%20in%20the%2021st%20century.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20death%20count%20of%2018%2C500%20was%20later%20revised%20upwards%20by%20The%20Lancet%20medical%20journal%20to%20between%20151%2C700%20and%20575%2C400%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701096060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-03%2Fegmkjiqg_influenza-generic_625x300_04_March_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-confirms-first-human-case-of-swine-flu-strain-h1n2-similar-circulating-in-pigs-health-agency-4611160%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22UK%20public%20health%20officials%20on%20Monday%20said%20they%20had%20confirmed%20a%20first%20human%20case%20of%20a%20swine%20flu%20strain%20similar%20to%20one%20that%20has%20been%20circulating%20in%20pigs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-confirms-first-human-case-of-swine-flu-strain-h1n2-similar-circulating-in-pigs-health-agency-4611160%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-confirms-first-human-case-of-swine-flu-strain-h1n2-similar-circulating-in-pigs-health-agency-4611160%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-confirms-first-human-case-of-swine-flu-strain-h1n2-similar-circulating-in-pigs-health-agency-4611160%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEvery%20Player%20Wants%20To...%26quot%3B%3A%20Star%20Pak%20Pacer%20Expresses%20Desire%20To%20Play%20In%20IPL%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPa