ed%20the%20vendors%20falls%20under%20a%20no-vending%20zone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20civic%20body%20said%20the%20action%20was%20taken%20to%20check%20illegal%20encroachment%20and%20ensure%20smooth%20flow%20of%20traffic%20on%20the%20road%2C%20which%20is%20close%20to%20the%20political%20power%20centre%20of%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20move%20has%20hit%20the%20Kashmiri%20vendors%2C%20who%20come%20all%20the%20way%20from%20the%20valley%20at%20the%20onset%20of%20winter%20every%20year%20to%20sell%20dry%20fruits%20and%20earn%20a%20livelihood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20fourth%20incident%20since%202019%20in%20which%20the%20business%20of%20Kashmiri%20vendors%20was%20obstructed%20either%20by%20the%20police%20and%20municipal%20corporations%20or%20by%20right-wing%20vigilante%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20they%20come%20from%20so%20far%2C%20yet%20offer%20good%20quality%20dry%20fruits%20at%20rates%20cheaper%20than%20those%20available%20in%20the%20markets%2C%20they%20feel%20the%20administration%20should%20be%20more%20compassionate%20towards%20them.%20They%20want%20the%20administration%20to%20allot%20them%20designated%20places%20to%20sell%20their%20products%2C%20so%20that%20the%20local%20authorities%20don%E2%80%99t%20exploit%20or%20intimidate%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20clean%20people%20and%20sit%20%5Bon%20the%20roadside%5D%20like%20open%20books.%C2%A0%20For%20two%20to%20three%20months%2C%20we%20adorn%20the%20roads%20of%20Lucknow%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20dry%20fruits%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dar%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDar%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20the%20Kulgam%20district%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20for%20the%20past%2015%20to%2016%20years%2C%20he%20has%20been%20visiting%20Lucknow%20to%20sell%20dry%20fruits%20and%20other%20items%2C%20including%20almonds%2C%20raisins%2C%20pistachios%2C%20cashews%2C%20apricots%2C%20figs%20and%20saffron.%20The%20business%20in%20the%20valley%20is%20disrupted%20in%20the%20winter%20months%20due%20to%20heavy%20snowfall%2C%20and%20markets%20in%20other%20cities%2C%20like%20Delhi%2C%20are%20saturated.%20These%20Kashmiri%20vendors%20find%20Lucknow%2C%20which%20is%20known%20for%20its%20composite%20culture%20and%20peaceful%20atmosphere%2C%20an%20ideal%20place%20for%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20path.%20We%20have%20no%20other%20option.%20Otherwise%2C%20why%20would%20we%20tolerate%20such%20insults%20every%20time%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Dar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202019%2C%20Dar%20was%20among%20a%20group%20of%20Kashmiri%20dry%20fruit%20traders%20who%20alleged%20that%20the%20UP%20police%20harassed%20them%20and%20did%20not%20allow%20them%20to%20sell%20their%20products%20on%20the%20roadside%20in%20Lucknow.%20They%20also%20accused%20the%20police%20of%20snatching%20their%20Aadhaar%20cards%20without%20offering%20any%20explanation%2C%20and%20confiscating%20their%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20said%20that%20these%20vendors%20were%20selling%20their%20products%20in%20a%20no-vending%20zone%20and%20that%20the%20restrictions%20had%20been%20imposed%20due%20to%20security%20arrangements%20made%20during%20the%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202019%2C%20two%20Kashmiri%20vendors%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Farchive%2Fin%2Fentry%2Fkashmiri-dry-fruit-sellers-attacked-in-lucknow-by-saffron-clad-men_in_5c80a224e4b06ff26ba596c5%5C%22%3Ewere%20assaulted%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20saffron-clad%20men%20at%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20Daliganj%20bridge%2C%20where%20vendors%20set%20up%20stalls%20to%20sell%20vegetables%2C%20fruits%20and%20other%20items.%20The%20vendors%20%E2%80%93%20Abdus%20Salam%20and%20Mohammad%20Afzal%20Naik%20%E2%80%93%20were%20slapped%2C%20beaten%20up%20with%20sticks%20and%20also%20subjected%20to%20verbal%20abuses%20and%20anti-Kashmiri%20remarks.%20The%20men%20called%20them%20%E2%80%9Cterrorists%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cstone-pelters%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0They%20also%20recorded%20the%20incident%20on%20their%20phones%20and%20circulated%20the%20videos%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20led%20to%20widespread%20outrage%2C%20following%20which%20the%20police%20arrested%20four%20persons%20associated%20with%20a%20lesser-known%20right-wing%20group%2C%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Dal%20Trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20an%20incident%20was%20unheard%20of%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20and%20even%20the%20UP%20police%20took%20cognizance%20of%20it%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20and%20issued%20an%20alert%20in%20the%20state%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20was%20not%20repeated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20had%20happened%20despite%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fno-fresh-incidents-of-violence-against-kashmiris-centre-tells-supreme-court%2Farticle26383313.ece%5C%22%3ESupreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20directions%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20all%20states%20and%20Union%20territories%20to%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20Kashmiris%2C%20amid%20reports%20of%20them%20being%20targeted%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20February%202019%20Pulwama%20attack%2C%20in%20which%20more%20than%2040%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20personnel%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98They%20say%20they%20want%20Kashmir%2C%20but%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20like%20Kashmiris%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20in%20February%2C%20some%20persons%20who%20were%20allegedly%20staff%20of%20the%20municipal%20corporation%20misbehaved%20with%20a%20group%20of%20Kashmiri%20vendors%20and%20threw%20their%20bags%20into%20the%20Gomti%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%20said%20he%20is%20still%20rattled%20by%20the%20unruly%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20municipality%20officials%20bundled%20up%20their%20goods%20into%20their%20vehicles%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20from%20the%20Samtamulak%20Crossing.%20Since%20the%20vendors%2C%20who%20were%20scared%20due%20to%20such%20bad%20experience%2C%20thought%20they%20would%20lose%20all%20their%20goods%2C%20they%20insisted%20that%20the%20officials%20allow%20them%20to%20travel%20with%20the%20confiscated%20goods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20they%20really%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20allow%20us%20to%20do%20business%20here%2C%20they%20should%20have%20put%20up%20a%20notice%20saying%20%E2%80%98Kashmiris%20cannot%20sell%20things%20at%20this%20location.%E2%80%99%20Why%20%5Bare%20they%5D%20harassing%20us%20now%20when%20for%20the%20past%20month%20we%20have%20been%20selling%20our%20things%20at%20the%20same%20place%2C%20quietly%3F%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Ahmad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20the%20incident%2C%20these%20Kashmiris%20chose%20to%20stay%20put%20in%20their%20rented%20apartments%20rather%20than%20risk%20having%20their%20goods%20confiscated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20administration%20didn%E2%80%99t%20inform%20them%20about%20a%20%E2%80%98vending%20zone%E2%80%99%20where%20they%20can%20sell%20their%20goods%2C%20they%20are%20confused%20and%20worried.%20They%20came%20to%20Lucknow%20with%20the%20hope%20that%20they%20would%20be%20able%20to%20exhaust%20their%20items%20and%20earn%20a%20decent%20income%20before%20returning%20to%20their%20native%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20goods%20worth%20several%20lakh%20rupees.%20If%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20sell%20them%2C%20we%20stand%20to%20lose%20both%20them%20and%20the%20money%20we%20spent%20on%20transporting%20them%20here%2C%20along%20with%20the%20costs%20of%20rent%20and%20GST.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20know%20where%20to%20go%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ahmad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmad%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20Kulgam%20in%20South%20Kashmir%2C%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20conflict-affected%20districts%20in%20the%20region%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years%2C%20said%20the%20lack%20of%20livelihood%20opportunities%20and%20shortage%20of%20private%20jobs%20push%20young%20men%20like%20him%20to%20travel%20outside%20and%20earn%20a%20living%20as%20hawkers%20and%20vendors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20like%20it%20when%20we%20get%20abused%20here.%20We%20also%20have%20self-respect.%20But%20we%20are%20helpless%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20say%20they%20like%20and%20want%20Kashmir.%20But%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20like%20Kashmiris.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDar%20said%20that%20although%20he%20never%20faced%20such%20harassment%20in%20the%20past%2C%20it%20had%20become%20a%20routine%20over%20the%20past%20five%20to%20six%20years%2C%20coinciding%20with%20the%20rule%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20in%20the%20state.%20However%2C%20the%20Kashmiri%20vendors%20said%20that%20they%20receive%20a%20lot%20of%20support%20from%20the%20local%20population%2C%20with%20whom%20they%20have%20built%20a%20relationship%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fhindutva-ecosystem-muslim-fruit-sellers-threat-india%5C%22%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Hindutva%20Ecosystem%E2%80%99%20Has%20a%20New%20Anti-Muslim%20Narrative.%20This%20Time%20Street%20Vendors%20Are%20the%20Target.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20did%20the%20authorities%20say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20Students%20Association%2C%20a%20group%20that%20raises%20issues%20of%20young%20Kashmiris%20studying%20or%20working%20in%20other%20parts%20of%20India%2C%20have%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20latest%20incident.%20Its%20national%20convenor%2C%20Nasir%20Khuehami%2C%20said%20that%20the%20municipal%20authorities%20had%20been%20seizing%20dry%20fruits%20daily%2C%20arbitrarily%20loading%20them%20onto%20vehicles%20and%20returning%20only%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20goods.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20recurring%20act%20has%20led%20to%20substantial%20financial%20losses%20for%20the%20sellers%2C%20who%20are%20already%20grappling%20with%20the%20challenges%20of%20earning%20a%20livelihood%20away%20from%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Association%20raised%20the%20matter%20with%20the%20office%20of%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath.%20Khuehami%20urged%20Awanish%20Awasthi%2C%20the%20chief%20advisor%20of%20Adityanath%2C%20for%20urgent%20intervention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Association%20said%20that%20Awasthi%20had%20assured%20them%20of%20full%20cooperation%20and%20informed%20them%20that%20all%20vendors%20would%20need%20permission%20from%20the%20municipal%20authorities%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Lucknow%20mayor%20Sushma%20Kharakwal%20claimed%20that%20there%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20any%20controversy%20over%20the%20Kashmiri%20vendors%20not%20being%20allowed%20to%20spread%20their%20wares%20on%20the%20roadside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20asked%20to%20go%20from%20there%20because%20a%20fleet%20(of%20VVIP%20cars)%20was%20passing%20by%20that%20way.%20The%20chief%20minister%20and%20the%20governor%20travel%20from%20that%20route%20and%20sitting%20on%20the%20road%20and%20selling%20items%20is%20not%20allowed%20for%20anyone%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kharakwal%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20laws%20against%20encroachment%20are%20the%20same%20for%20everyone%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20Kashmiris%20or%20locals.%20When%20asked%20if%20the%20municipality%20corporation%20would%20arrange%20a%20designated%20vending%20zone%20for%20the%20vendors%2C%20as%20desired%20by%20them%2C%20Kharakwal%20did%20not%20provide%20a%20clear%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701093659000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27181439%2Fpexels-mehran-b-86649.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffrustration-kashmiri-dry-fruit-vendors-lucknow-roadside-stalls%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%9CThey%20say%20they%20like%20and%20want%20Kashmir.%20But%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20like%20Kashmiris%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20vendor%20told%20The