allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FuBmC7JqEorU%3Fsi%3DDrTun4mUkY8KQyGx%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Mawasi%20lacks%20essential%20infrastructure.%20There%20are%20no%20hospitals%20and%20the%20vast%20majority%20of%20people%2C%20if%20pushed%20there%2C%20will%20have%20to%20live%20in%20tents.%20This%20will%20be%20at%20a%20time%20when%20winter%20has%20set%20in%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20cold%20and%20it%20rains%20frequently.%20Yet%2C%20Avichay%20Adraee%2C%20an%20Israeli%20defence%20forces%20spokesman%20has%20told%20the%20Arabic%20media%20(as%20reported%20by%20Paul%20Adams%20in%20his%20BBC%20story)%20al-Mawasi%20will%20provide%20%E2%80%9Cappropriate%20conditions%20for%20your%20loved%20ones%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdam%20says%3A%20%E2%80%9CIsraeli%20officials%20say%20it%20will%20be%20up%20to%20aid%20agencies%20to%20make%20sure%20help%20reaches%20al-Mawasi.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20heads%20of%2018%20UN%20agencies%20and%20NGOs%20have%20clearly%20rejected%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20plans.%20They%20issued%20a%20statement%20to%20say%3A%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20establishment%20of%20any%20safe%20zone%20in%20Gaza%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20the%20WHO%2C%20has%20called%20the%20idea%20of%20cramming%202%20million%20people%20into%20an%20area%20just%202.5%20kilometres%20by%204%20%E2%80%9Ca%20recipe%20for%20disaster%E2%80%9D.%20He%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CAttempting%20to%20cram%20so%20many%20people%20into%20such%20a%20small%20area%20with%20such%20little%20infrastructure%20or%20services%20will%20significantly%20increase%20risks%20to%20health%20for%20people%20who%20are%20already%20on%20the%20brink.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20happens%2C%20for%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%20this%20will%20be%20a%20second%20nakba.%20The%20first%20was%20in%201948%20when%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20homes%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20ended%20up%20as%20refugees%20in%20Gaza.%20Now%2C%2075%20years%20later%2C%20they%20have%20already%20been%20forced%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20in%20Gaza%20and%20could%20end%20up%20in%20a%20wee%20patch%20of%20land%20called%20al-Mawasi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20second%20trauma%20looming%20over%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%2C%20when%20the%20truce%20ends%2C%20is%20the%20real%20possibility%20that%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20could%20be%20considerably%20worse%20than%20what%20we%20saw%20during%20the%20first%2050%20days%20of%20the%20war.%20This%20is%20because%20Eli%20Cohen%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Foreign%20Minister%2C%20has%20already%20accepted%20that%20Israel%20only%20has%202-3%20weeks%20to%20obliterate%20Hamas%20before%20international%20pressure%20becomes%20impossible%20for%20Israel%20to%20resist.%20This%20clearly%20leaves%20open%20the%20prospect%20of%20a%20far%20higher%20and%20worse%20scale%20of%20bombing%20than%20we%20saw%20in%20the%20first%2050%20days%20of%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20hope%20that%20both%20the%20al-Mawasi%20project%20and%20the%20sharp%20increase%20in%20bombing%20that%20are%20anticipated%20after%20the%20truce%20ends%20will%20not%20happen%20or%20be%20substantially%20tempered%20is%20that%20pressure%20from%20Western%20governments%20%E2%80%93%20and%20perhaps%20behind%20that%20pressure%20from%20their%20people%20on%20those%20governments%20%E2%80%93%20is%20so%20strong%20that%20the%20Israel%20government%20is%20forced%20to%20re-think.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701093183000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27191652%2FKT-27-Nov-B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-why-israels-reported-resettlement-plan-for-gaza-could-amount-to-a-holocaust%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20plan%20is%20to%20push%20up%20to%202%20million