for%20a%20short%20break%20during%20the%20truce%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%2C%20but%20amid%20the%20laughter%2C%20their%20parents%20could%20not%20forget%20the%20hardships%20of%20war%20and%20homelessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20children%20splashed%20in%20the%20shallow%20water%2C%20jumping%20over%20small%20waves%2C%20adults%20in%20bare%20feet%20watched%20from%20the%20shore.%20Asmaa%20al-Sultan%2C%20a%20displaced%20woman%20from%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20sat%20on%20the%20sand%20with%20her%20arm%20around%20her%20mother.%20The%20older%20woman%20was%20crying%20quietly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2030%20members%20of%20the%20al-Sultan%20family%20are%20sheltering%20in%20a%20U.N.%20school%20in%20the%20town%20of%20Deir%20Al-Balah%20with%20hundreds%20of%20other%20displaced%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20came%20to%20the%20beach%20to%20take%20a%20breather%2C%20to%20escape%20from%20the%20feeling%20of%20the%20crowded%20schools%20and%20from%20the%20depressing%20and%20polluted%20environment%20we%20are%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Asmaa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F6b7a9jc_gaza-beach_625x300_27_November_23.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20come%20to%20the%20beach%20to%20relax%2C%20to%20swim%2C%20for%20their%20children%20to%20have%20fun%2C%20they%20take%20food%20with%20them.%20But%20we%20are%20so%20depressed.%20We%20are%20on%20the%20beach%20but%20we%20want%20to%20cry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20have%20left%20their%20homes%20in%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20which%20has%20borne%20the%20brunt%20of%20Israel's%20military%20assault%2C%20to%20seek%20refuge%20in%20tents%2C%20schools%20or%20the%20homes%20of%20friends%20and%20relatives%20in%20the%20southern%20part%20of%20the%20strip.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gruelling%20conditions%20in%20the%20tent%20camps%20and%20schools%2C%20with%20overcrowding%2C%20a%20dearth%20of%20toilets%20and%20showers%2C%20and%20long%20daily%20queues%20for%20small%20rations%20of%20food%20and%20water%2C%20have%20been%20compounded%20by%20the%20psychological%20impact%20of%20bombardment%20and%20displacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20beach%20at%20Deir%20Al-Balah%20has%20a%20row%20of%20fishermen's%20huts%20at%20the%20back%2C%20towards%20the%20bottom%20of%20a%20slope%20strewn%20with%20rubbish.%20Some%20displaced%20people%20had%20taken%20up%20residence%20in%20the%20flimsy%20huts%2C%20clothes%20hanging%20on%20strings%20outside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'What%20Happens%20To%20Us%20Next%3F'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaleed%20al-Sultan%2C%20one%20of%20Asmaa's%20younger%20relatives%2C%20was%20trying%20to%20untangle%20a%20net%20near%20the%20huts%20as%20he%20prepared%20to%20go%20out%20fishing%20in%20a%20small%20boat%2C%20hoping%20the%20truce%20would%20mean%20he%20could%20do%20so%20without%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20brought%20nothing%20with%20me%20when%20I%20was%20displaced%2C%20so%20I%20thought%20I%20would%20make%20a%20living%20from%20fishing%2C%20but%20the%20(Israeli)%20guards%20stopped%20me%20and%20started%20shooting%20at%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20war%20began%20when%20Hamas%20burst%20out%20of%20Gaza%20on%20Oct.%207%20and%20rampaged%20through%20southern%20Israel%2C%20killing%201%2C200%20people%2C%20including%20babies%20and%20children%2C%20and%20seizing%20240%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20responded%20with%20an%20all-out%20assault%20on%20Gaza%20which%20has%20killed%2014%2C800%20Palestinians%2C%20four%20in%20ten%20of%20them%20children%20under%2018%2C%20according%20to%20health%20officials%20in%20the%20Hamas-controlled%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20displaced%20people%20have%20seized%20the%20opportunity%20of%20the%20four-day%20truce%2C%20which%20began%20on%20Friday%2C%20to%20check%20on%20their%20homes%2C%20others%20have%20been%20too%20fearful%20to%20return%20to%20the%20north%2C%20much%20of%20which%20has%20been%20reduced%20to%20a%20wasteland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20afraid%20about%20the%20end%20of%20these%20four%20days.%20We%20don't%20know%20what%20will%20happen%20to%20us%20next%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hazem%20al-Sultan%2C%20Asmaa's%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20they%20and%20their%20relatives%20had%20not%20dared%20to%20head%20north%20for%20fear%20of%20being%20shot%20at%20by%20Israeli%20soldiers%2C%20and%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20state%20their%20homes%20might%20be%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20afraid%20for%20our%20children%2C%20for%20ourselves%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20know%20what%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701092820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fp1trh7t_gaza-beach-children_120x90_27_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-truce-deal-tears-and-laughter-on-gaza-beach-as-children-get-break-from-war-4610945%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Children%20played%20on%20a%20Gaza%20beach%20as%20displaced%20families%20left%20their%20cramped%20shelters%20for%20a%20short%20break%20during%20the%20truce%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%2C%20but%20amid%20the%20laughter%2C%20their%20parents%20could%20not%20forget%20the%20hardships%20of%20war%20and%20homelessness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-hamas-truce-deal-tears-and-laughter-on-gaza-beach-as-children-get-break-from-war-4610945%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworl