ttps%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27190000%2Fimage-1550.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%202024%20edition%20of%20the%20Biennale%20f%C3%BCr%20aktuelle%20Fotografie%2C%20a%20contemporary%20photo%20exhibition%2C%20curated%20by%20Shahidul%20Alam%2C%20Tanzim%20Wahab%20and%20Munem%20Wasif%2C%20has%20been%20cancelled%20due%20to%20Shahidul%E2%80%99s%20Facebook%20posts%20in%20support%20of%20Palestine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20curators%20were%20informed%20of%20the%20cancellation%20through%20a%20press%20release%20on%20November%2023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tenth%20edition%20of%20the%20exhibition%20was%20due%20to%20be%20held%20in%20the%20German%20cities%20of%20Mannheim%2C%20Ludwigshafen%20and%20Heidelberg%2C%20in%20March%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Biennale%E2%80%99s%20press%20release%2C%20as%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theartnewspaper.com%2F2023%2F11%2F22%2Fgerman-photo-biennial-cancelled-after-curators-posts-are-deemed-antisemitic%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EArt%20Newspaper%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EAlam%20critical%20posts%20about%20the%20Israeli%20military%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20in%20Gaza%20on%20social%20media%20prompted%20the%20decision.%20Alam%E2%80%99s%20Facebook%20page%20contained%20%E2%80%9Ccontent%20that%20can%20be%20read%20as%20antisemitic%20and%20antisemitic%20content%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20event%E2%80%99s%20organisers%20alleged%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20a%20charge%20that%20Alam%20and%20his%20colleagues%20have%20refuted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20were%20invited%20to%20curate%20the%20Biennale%20because%20they%20claimed%20they%20wanted%20our%20voice%2C%20and%20our%20perspective%20on%20how%20we%20see%20the%20world.%20But%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20crisis%2C%20it%20has%20appeared%20that%20our%20voices%20were%20only%20invited%20on%20their%20terms%2C%20subservient%20to%20their%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlam%20is%20a%20photojournalist%20based%20in%20Dhaka%20who%20has%20been%20actively%20posting%20on%20social%20media%20since%20October%207%2C%20when%20Hamas%20militants%20invaded%20Israeli%20territory%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Farticle%2Fisrael-hostages-hamas-explained.html%5C%22%3Eresulting%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20approximately%201%2C200%20deaths%20and%20the%20taking%20of%20over%20200%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biennale%20organisers%20released%20a%20statement%20saying%20they%20voiced%20concerns%20to%20Alam%20and%20the%20festival%E2%80%99s%20other%20curators%2C%20Bangladeshi%20photographers%20Tanzim%20Wahab%20and%20Munem%20Wasif%2C%20in%20attempts%20to%20%E2%80%9Csensitise%20%5Bthem%5D%20to%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20special%20historical%20responsibility%20for%20the%20state%20of%20Israel%20and%20its%20right%20to%20exist.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20Alam%20continued%20to%20post%20pro-Palestinian%20content%20because%20he%20%E2%80%9Csees%20himself%20as%20an%20activist%20and%20demands%20freedom%20of%20expression.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Wahab%20and%20Wasif%20said%20they%20would%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20Biennale%20without%20Alam%2C%20the%20newspaper%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20consequences%20of%20the%20cancellation%20for%20the%20Biennale%20f%C3%BCr%20aktuelle%20Fotografie%20and%20the%20organising%20team%20are%20far-reaching.%20They%20jeopardise%20the%20future%20of%20the%20entire%20event.%20In%20the%20time%20ahead%2C%20we%20will%20do%20everything%20in%20our%20power%20to%20maintain%20the%20Biennale%20as%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20and%20most%20important%20photography%20events%20in%20Germany%20and%20Europe%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20organisers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20the%20curators%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CSince%2015%20October%2C%20we%20had%20been%20in%20multiple%20discussions%20with%20the%20Biennale%20management%20regarding%20social%20media%20posts%20made%20by%20Shahidul%20Alam%2C%20on%20his%20Facebook%20account%2C%20related%20to%20the%20ongoing%20war%20crimes%20in%20Gaza.%20While%20the%20posts%20were%20a%20response%20to%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20Israeli%20government%2C%20the%20Biennale%20incorrectly%20equated%20these%20to%20anti-Semitism.%20We%20feel%20that%20the%20failure%20to%20draw%20a%20distinction%20between%20criticism%20of%20a%20government%20and%20of%20a%20people%2C%20is%20irresponsible%20and%20damaging%20to%20the%20honesty%20of%20public%20discourse.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20times%20of%20crisis%2C%20cultural%20institutions%20are%20meant%20to%20create%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20careful%20listening%2C%20with%20and%20despite%20our%20differences.%20The%20very%20institution%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20host%20us%2C%20and%20make%20space%20for%20diverse%20voices%2C%20has%20slandered%20their%20invited%20curators.%20Many%20of%20us%2C%20from%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20who%20are%20invited%20to%20work%20with%20Western%20institutions%2C%20on%20the%20premise%20of%20inclusivity%2C%20often%20share%20this%20scepticism%20%E2%80%93%20of%20how%20far%20our%20diversity%20is%20being%20tokenised%20or%20instrumentalised%20for%20course%20correction%20of%20their%20historical%20legacies%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20truly%20welcoming%20are%20these%20institutions%20towards%20radically%20different%20ways%20of%20thinking%2C%20which%20emerge%20from%20vastly%20different%20contexts%2C%20both%20contemporary%20and%20historical%3F%20Have%20we%20lost%20the%20basic%20human%20right%20to%20question%2C%20protest%2C%20or%20collectively%20mourn%3F%E2%80%9D%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20the%20curatorial%20advisors%20of%20Biennale%20have%20criticised%20the%20move%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwitch%20hunting%20practice%E2%80%9D%2C%20taking%20place%20in%20German%20cultural%20institutions%20for%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20disdainful%20form%20of%20scapegoating%20of%20Shahidul%20Alam%20and%20many%20others%20is%20outright%20censorship%3B%20it%20is%20racist%20and%20discriminatory.%20The%20ease%20and%20callousness%20with%20which%20these%20type%20of%20accusations%20are%20pronounced%20in%20Germany%20these%20days%20suggests%20that%20fascism%20is%20returning%20to%20the%20present%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20comes%20just%20a%20week%20after%20a%20similar%20controversy%20involving%20the%20international%20art%20festival%20Documenta%20in%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20Kassel%20resulted%20in%20the%20resignation%20of%20all%20six%20Finding%20Committee%20members.%20Ranjit%20Hoskote%2C%20a%20writer%20and%20curator%20based%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20faced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fcurator-ranjit-hoskote-resigns-from-documentas-finding-committee-over-anti-semitism-allegations%5C%22%3Eallegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20anti-Semitism%20due%20to%20his%20endorsement%20of%20a%20Boycott%2C%20Divestment%2C%20and%20Sanctions%20petition%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20accusations%2C%20he%20stepped%20down%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20feel%2C%20strongly%2C%20that%20I%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20the%20proceedings%20of%20a%20kangaroo%20court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlam%20referred%20to%20the%20collective%20resignation%20letter%20from%20four%20of%20Hoskote%E2%80%99s%20colleagues%20as%20an%20expos%C3%A9%20of%20Germany%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cblinkered%20position%20on%20freedom%20of%20expression.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBelow%20are%20the%20full%20statements%20from%20the%20curators%20and%20curatorial%20advisors%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStatement%20by%20Curators%20of%20Biennale%20f%C3%BCr%20aktuelle%20Fotografie%202024%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20dismayed%20by%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Director%2C%20Yasmin%20Meinicke%2C%20and%20the%20Board%20of%20the%20Biennale%20f%C3%BCr%20aktuelle%20Fotografie%2C%20taken%20in%20consultation%20with%20German%20state%20authorities%20to%20unilaterally%20cancel%20the%202024%20edition.%20For%2018%20months%2C%20we%20worked%20with%2044%20artists%2C%20six%20partner%20organisations%2C%20three%20advisors%20and%20various%20colleagues%20to%20bring%20the%20Biennale%20to%20fruition.%20As%20the%20curators%2C%20we%20only%20found%20out%20about%20this%20cancellation%20through%20a%20press%20release%20in%20the%20public%20domain%2C%20published%20without%20our%20consent%2C%20on%2023%20November%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20find%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20Director%20and%20the%20Board%20of%20the%20Biennale%20to%20be%20a%20breach%20of%20trust%20and%20antithetical%20to%20the%20very%20premise%20of%20the%20theme%20we%20were%20intending%20to%20explore%20in%20this%20edition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20it%20is%20in%20violation%20of%20our%20contractual%20agreement%2C%20which%20states%2C%20%E2%80%9CAll%20press%20releases%20are%20published%20in%20agreement%20with%20the%20curator%20and%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20the%20Biennale.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20title%20of%20our%20edition%20was%20%E2%80%9CListening%20to%20Disquiet%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%20looked%20to%20address%20the%20question%20of%20what%20embodied%20listening%20may%20mean%E2%80%94as%20a%20precondition%20to%20forming%20opinions%E2%80%94in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20biennale.%20Our%20belief%20in%20social%20justice%2C%20our%20collective%20struggles%2C%20our%20friendships%2C%20our%20mutual%20losses%2C%20and%20our%20solidarity%20urge%20us%20to%20listen%20carefully.%20Not%20only%20to%20hear%2C%20but%20to%20absorb%20the%20range%20of%20frequencies%20emitted%20by%20this%20disquiet%2C%20and%20by%20the%20images%20produced%20by%20artists%20across%20geographies%20and%20temporalities.%20We%20are%20saddened%20that%20we%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20share%20our%20planned%20exhibition%20with%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%2015%20October%2C%20we%20had%20been%20in%20multiple%20discussions%20with%20the%20Biennale%20management%20regarding%20social%20media%20posts%20made%20by%20Shahidul%20Alam%2C%20on%20his%20Facebook%20account%2C%20related%20to%20the%20ongoing%20war%20crimes%20in%20Gaza.%20While%20the%20posts%20were%20a%20response%20to%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20Israeli%20government%2C%20the%20Biennale%20incorrectly%20equated%20these%20to%20anti-Semitism.%20We%20feel%20that%20the%20failure%20to%20draw%20a%20distinction%20between%20criticism%20of%20a%20government%20and%20of%20a%20people%2C%20is%20irresponsible%20and%20damaging%20to%20the%20honesty%20of%20public%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20in-person%20discussions%20in%20Mannheim%2C%20in%20the%20week%20of%2023%20October%2C%20several%20partners%20to%20the%20biennale%E2%80%94including%20multiple%20directors%20of%20associated%20institutions%2C%20some%20members%20of%20the%20Board%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Biennale%20team%20expressed%20their%20disagreement%20with%20the%20position%20of%20the%20director%20on%20these%20social%20media%20posts.%20Several%20members%20of%20the%20Biennale%20team%20voiced%20their%20indignation%20at%20the%20developing%20atmosphere%20of%20self-censorship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20series%20of%20communications%2C%20we%20were%20informed%20on%2014%20November%20that%20we%20could%20continue%20as%20curators%20of%20the%20upcoming%20edition.%20Yet%2C%20on%2023%20November%2C%20the%20Biennale%20Director%2C%20after%20meeting%20with%20the%20mayors%20of%20cultural%20affairs%20of%20all%20three%20cities%20in%20which%20the%20Biennale%20was%20to%20be%20held%E2%80%94Mannheim%2C%20Ludwigshafen%20and%20Heidelberg%E2%80%94sent%20a%20press%20release%2C%20unilaterally%20announcing%20the%20cancellation%20of%20the%20event.%20The%20director%20did%20not%20seek%20to%20challenge%20state%20censorship%20or%20to%20fulfil%20her%20role%20as%20a%20leader%20of%20the%20inviting%20institution%2C%20to%20exercise%20care%20towards%20the%20curators%2C%20and%20in%20turn%20the%20artists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20where%20there%20has%20been%20an%20indefensible%20escalation%20in%20relentless%20brutalities%20against%20the%20Palestinian%20people%2C%20we%20believe%20that%20we%20have%20a%20moral%20responsibility%20to%20decide%20which%20side%20of%20history%20we%20will%20stand%20on.%20Recent%20events%20have%20led%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20civilians%20on%20both%20the%20Israeli%20and%20Palestinian%20side%2C%20which%20we%20have%20stood%20against%2C%20and%20continue%20to%20condemn.%20However%2C%20we%20cannot%20ignore%20the%20disproportionate%20toll%20on%20Palestinians%20now%20and%20historically%20since%201948.%20For%20us%20to%20disregard%20this%20stark%20difference%E2%80%94in%20the%20number%20of%20Palestinians%20killed%2C%20their%20homes%20destroyed%2C%20their%20basic%20civil%20liberties%20curtailed%20by%20the%20State%20of%20Israel%E2%80%94would%20be%20to%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20unfolding%20realities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOur%20acknowledgment%20of%20the%20history%20of%20the%20Palestinian%20cause%2C%20and%20the%20present%20assault%20in%20Gaza%20on%20civilians%2C%20does%20not%2C%20in%20any%20way%2C%20translate%20to%20us%20dismissing%20the%20historical%20persecution%20of%20the%20Jewish%20people.%20Such%20a%20conflation%20is%20a%20deliberate%20and%20dangerous%20misreading%20of%20our%20position.%20It%20is%20this%20shrinking%20space%20for%20care%20towards%20the%20persecution%20of%20any%20community%2C%20that%20we%20seek%20to%20address%20in%20the%20critical%20space%20of%20arts%2C%20education%2C%20and%20discourse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20times%20of%20crisis%2C%20cultural%20institutions%20are%20meant%20to%20create%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20careful%20listening%2C%20with%20and%20despite%20our%20differences.%20The%20very%20institution%20that%20was%20supposed%20to%20host%20us%2C%20and%20make%20space%20for%20diverse%20voices%2C%20has%20slandered%20their%20invited%20curators.%20Many%20of%20us%2C%20from%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20who%20are%20invited%20to%20work%20with%20Western%20institutions%2C%20on%20the%20premise%20of%20inclusivity%2C%20often%20share%20this%20skepticism%E2%80%94of%20how%20far%20our%20diversity%20is%20being%20tokenised%20or%20instrumentalised%20for%20course%20correction%20of%20their%20historical%20legacies.%20How%20truly%20welcoming%20are%20these%20institutions%20towards%20radically%20different%20ways%20of%20thinking%2C%20which%20emerge%20from%20vastly%20different%20contexts%2C%20both%20contemporary%20and%20historical%3F%20Have%20we%20lost%20the%20basic%20human%20right%20to%20question%2C%20protest%2C%20or%20collectively%20mourn%3F%20Our%20difference%20of%20perspective%E2%80%94shaped%20by%20our%20colonial%20past%E2%80%94in%20reading%20history%20and%20its%20contemporary%20fallouts%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20reason%20to%20educate%20or%20%E2%80%9Csensitize%E2%80%9D%20us.%20We%20were%20invited%20to%20curate%20the%20Biennale%20because%20they%20claimed%20they%20wanted%20our%20voice%2C%20and%20our%20perspective%20on%20how%20we%20see%20the%20world.%20But%20in%20a%20moment%20of%20crisis%2C%20it%20has%20appeared%20that%20our%20voices%20were%20only%20invited%20on%20their%20terms%2C%20subservient%20to%20their%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECensorship%20cannot%20separate%20the%20waves%20of%20communication%20by%20force.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20take%20the%20initiative%20to%20listen%20differently%20in%20our%20own%20communities.%20Space%20must%20be%20created.%20Creating%20true%20pluralism%20by%20moving%20beyond%20our%20individual%20comfort%20zones%20is%20part%20of%20a%20long%20struggle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EShahidul%20Alam%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3ETanzim%20Wahab%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cem%3EMunem%20Wasif%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStatement%20by%20curatorial%20advisors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3Eof%20Biennale%20f%C3%BCr%20aktuelle%20Fotografie%202024%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accusation%20of%20anti-semitism%20against%20Dr.%20Shahidul%20Alam%20comes%20as%20no%20surprise.%20It%20is%20the%20logical%20continuation%20of%20a%20witch%20hunting%20practice%20taking%20place%20in%20German%20cultural%20institutions%20for%20several%20years%20now%20(at%20least%20since%20early%202020%20when%20Achille%20Mbembe%20was%20desinvited%20from%20the%20Ruhrtriennale).%20It%20reveals%20the%20incapacity%20of%20Germany%20and%20its%20institutions%20to%20deal%20with%20its%20own%20past%2C%20to%20deal%20with%20conflict%2C%20and%20to%20question%20its%20self-awarded%20chronic%20superiority%20and%20entitlement%20%E2%80%94%20even%20in%20a%20context%20in%20which%20the%20object%20of%20its%C2%A0Staatsraison%C2%A0has%20clearly%20and%20publicly%20stated%20genocidal%20intent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20disdainful%20form%20of%20scapegoating%20of%20Dr.%20Shahidul%20Alam%20and%20many%20others%20is%20outright%20censorship%2C%20it%20is%20racist%20and%20discriminatory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ease%20and%20callousness%20with%20which%20these%20type%20of%20accusations%20are%20pronounced%20in%20Germany%20these%20days%20suggests%20that%20fascism%20is%20returning%20to%20the%20present.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%20we%20should%20all%20actively%20refuse%20to%20contribute%20to%20cultural%20labour%20in%20Germany!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYasmine%20Eid%20Sabbagh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20often%20see%20western%C2%A0cultural%20institutions%20call%20upon%20the%20labour%20of%20many%2C%20under%20the%20ostensible%20premise%20of%20supporting%20a%C2%A0diversity%20of%20voices%20and%20fostering%20critical%20thought.%C2%A0However%2C%20this%20decision%20of%20the%C2%A0Biennale%C2%A0to%20cancel%20an%20entire%C2%A0an%20entire%20edition%C2%A0over%20Shahidul%E2%80%99s%20social%20media%20posts%C2%A0and%20to%20communicate%20it%C2%A0through%20a%20press%20release%20before%C2%A0they%20even%20personally%20informed%20the%20curators%2C%20reveals%20a%20hierarchical%20mindset.%20By%20offering%20an%20invitation%2C%20it%20is%20assumed%20that%C2%A0they%20define%20the%20parameters%20of%20this%20diversity%2C%20and%20a%20critical%20lens%20can%20be%20used%20to%20view%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%20but%20not%20themselves.%C2%A0It%20is%20worth%20asking%20then%2C%20if%20these%20so-called%20collaborations%20are%20meant%20for%20toeing%20the%20institutional%20line%20and%20if%20those%20invited%20must%20express%20gratitude%2C%20in%20so%20far%20as%2C%20posing%20no%20challenge%20to%20that%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20censorship%2C%20the%20Western%20liberal%20democracy%2C%20with%20its%20supposed%20tenets%20of%20free%20speech%20and%20expression%2C%20is%20exposing%20its%20racist%C2%A0double-standards%E2%80%94valuing%20the%20rights%20of%20some%20communities%20above%20others.%C2%A0In%20selectively%20acknowledging%20history%2C%20and%20the%20persecution%20of%20only%20one%20set%20of%20people%2C%C2%A0it%20appears%20that%20Germany%20is%20seeking%20to%20absolve%20itself%20of%20its%20complicity%20in%20past%20events%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20another%20historical%20wrong%20in%20the%20making.%20I%20stand%20in%20full%20solidarity%20with%20all%20three%20curators%2C%20for%20having%20the%20courage%20to%20acknowledge%20the%20long%20arc%20of%20multiple%20histories%20and%20oppose%20the%20grotesque%20war%20crimes%20being%20committed%20by%20Israel%20in%20the%20present%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETanvi%20Mishra%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701092705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27190000%2Fimage-1550.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fgerman-photo-exhibition-cancelled-amid-anti-semitism-allegations-against-curators-facebook-posts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20announcement%20comes%20just%20a%20week%20after%20a%20similar%20controversy%20involving%20the%20international%20art%20festival%20Documenta%20in%20Germany's%20Kassel%20resulted%20in%20the%20resignation%20of%20all%20si