3A%20Grey%20Areas%20In%20Draft%20Broadcasting%20Regulation%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20draft%20broadcasting%20regulation%20bill%20drawn%20up%20by%20the%20Centre%20has%20set%20off%20a%20controversy%20with%20its%20provisions%20that%20draw%20not%20only%20broadcasting%20companies%20but%20also%20OTT%20platforms%2C%20digital%20news%20and%20apps%20into%20its%20ambit.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20seeks%20to%20directly%20regulate%20streaming%20platforms%20such%20as%20Netflix%2C%20Amazon%20Prime%20Video%20and%20Disney%2BHotstar%20as%20over-the-top%2C%20or%20OTT%2C%20broadcasting%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20even%20include%20social%20media%20platforms%20like%20What'sApp%2C%20and%20signal%20messaging%20companies.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20likelihood%20that%20it%20will%20also%20cover%20even%20individuals%20putting%20up%20news%20and%20current%20affairs%20content%20online%20on%20YouTube%20and%20other%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20grey%20area%20drew%20criticism%20as%20the%20bill%20was%20put%20up%20for%20public%20consultation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20be%20a%20content%20evaluation%20committee%20for%20self-regulation%20and%20broadcasting%20advisory%20council%20to%20advise%20central%20government%20on%20programme%20code%20and%20advertising%20code%20violations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20will%20replace%20Cable%20Television%20Network%20Act%20as%20well%20as%20a%20slew%20of%20policies%20and%20guidelines%20drawn%20up%20later%20to%20plug%20holes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20aims%20to%20have%20a%20self-regulation%20mechanism%20in%20terms%20of%20content%20and%20bring%20in%20a%20committee%20to%20guide%20the%20government%20in%20cases%20of%20complications.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20will%20also%20be%20an%20advisory%20council%20to%20advise%20the%20government%20in%20case%20of%20programming%20code%20violations.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20made%20provisions%20for%20pe