and%20woes%20heard%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20100%20of%20the%20145%20candidates%20who%20submitted%20their%20nominations%20from%20Gajwel%20belong%20to%20a%20group%20of%20people%20who%20say%20that%20their%20properties%20in%20Shankar%20Hills%2C%20an%20area%20on%20the%20western%20outskirts%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20were%20%E2%80%9Cstolen%E2%80%9D%20from%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20allege%20that%20the%20BRS%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frahul-gandhi-digitised-land-records-telangana%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Dharani%E2%80%99%20land%20management%20portal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20contributed%20to%20the%20problem.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVeeraiah%20Konduri%2C%20a%20lawyer%20associated%20with%20the%20group%20of%20nominees%2C%20said%20that%20these%20properties%20were%20captured%20and%20resold%20by%20the%20land%20mafia%20with%20the%20support%20of%20revenue%20officials%20starting%20in%201996%2C%20when%20construction%20on%20the%20lands%20was%20restricted%20due%20to%20their%20proximity%20to%20two%20important%20reservoirs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKonduri%20also%20said%20that%20though%20court%20orders%20have%20reaffirmed%20the%20rightful%20ownership%20of%20the%20properties%2C%20the%20Dharani%20portal%20misclassified%20them%20as%20agricultural%20land%20and%20issued%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epattadar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20passbooks%20to%20their%20erstwhile%20owners%20who%20sold%20them%20in%20the%201980s%20to%20the%20involved%20group%20of%20people.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMudragalla%20Nageshwar%20Rao%2C%20one%20of%20the%20nominees%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Ftelangana%2Fin-kcrs-gajwel-citadel-many-contest-against-him-just-to-draw-his-attention-to-their-woes%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20South%20First%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20news%20website%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20they%20wanted%20to%20throw%20light%20on%20their%20long-neglected%20problem.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20raised%20this%20issue%20multiple%20times%2C%20but%20no%20one%20paid%20heed.%20With%20over%20100%20people%20in%20the%20%5BShankar%20Hills%20Welfare%20Association%5D%2C%20we%20filed%20nominations%20against%20KCR%20to%20draw%20attention%20to%20the%20problem%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20South%20First%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20quoted%20him%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKonduri%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20most%20of%20the%20nominees%20withdrew%20from%20the%20contest%20after%20BRS%20leader%20and%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20health%20and%20finance%20minister%20T.%20Harish%20Rao%20assured%20them%20that%20the%20issue%20would%20be%20rectified.%20The%20nominations%20of%20some%20persons%20were%20rejected%20for%20irregularities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Frythu-bandhu-scheme-election-commission-brs%5C%22%3ETelangana%3A%20EC%20Withdraws%20Nod%20to%20BRS%20to%20Disburse%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20Scheme.%20What%20Does%20This%20Mean%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EFighting%20for%20those%20displaced%20by%20reservoirs%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20Telangana%20government%E2%80%99s%20flagship%20schemes%20is%20the%20Kaleshwaram%20Lift%20Irrigation%20Project%20(KLIP).%20Inaugurated%20in%202019%20and%20touted%20as%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20project%20of%20its%20kind%2C%20the%20KLIP%20pumps%20water%20from%20the%20low-lying%20Godavari%20river%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20north%20to%20higher%2C%20drought-prone%20areas%20in%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Telangana%20government%E2%80%99s%20process%20of%20acquiring%20land%20for%20the%20project%20has%20not%20been%20free%20from%20controversy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20one%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20state%20government%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fgovernment-violates-land-acquisition-laws-in-telangana-irrigation-project%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20been%20accused%20of%20trying%20to%20bypass%20a%202013%20Union%20government%20law%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20regulating%20land%20acquisition%20and%20rehabilitation%20for%20displaced%20persons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20has%20also%20been%20accused%20of%20providing%20inadequate%20compensation%20and%20poor-quality%20housing%20materials%20to%20people%20displaced%20by%20reservoirs%20that%20are%20part%20of%20the%20KLIP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKrishna%20Kumar%2C%20a%20man%20who%20used%20to%20live%20in%20a%20village%20submerged%20by%20the%20KLIP%E2%80%99s%20Kondapochamma%20reservoir%20and%20is%20now%20contesting%20from%20Gajwel%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthesouthfirst.com%2Ftelangana%2Fin-kcrs-gajwel-citadel-many-contest-against-him-just-to-draw-his-attention-to-their-woes%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etold%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20South%20First%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20state%20government%20coerced%20people%20to%20part%20with%20their%20lands.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20people%20received%20houses%20with%20poor%20construction%2C%20and%20now%2C%20with%20our%20own%20money%2C%20we%20are%20making%20repairs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kumar%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20South%20First%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20we%20refused%20to%20give%20away%20the%20lands%20for%20a%20lower%20package%2C%20a%20group%20of%2030%20%5BScheduled%20Caste%5D%20families%20filed%20court%20cases.%20In%20retaliation%2C%20the%20government%20forcefully%20evacuated%20the%20families%20and%20provided%20nothing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20nightmare%20for%20us%3B%20once%20we%20had%20everything%2C%20now%20we%E2%80%99re%20on%20the%20road%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27144627%2FAnnapurna-reservoir-1024x577.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27144627%2FAnnapurna-reservoir-1024x577.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27144627%2FAnnapurna-reservoir-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27144627%2FAnnapurna-reservoir.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-686554%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EReservoirs%20created%20as%20part%20of%20the%20KLIP%20have%20submerged%20multiple%20villages.%20Photo%3A%20irrigationpms.cgg.gov.in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDasari%20Chendramohan%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20Peddapalli%20district%20and%20another%20of%20Gajwel%E2%80%99s%2044%20remaining%20candidates%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20he%20was%20contesting%20the%20election%20to%20seek%20justice%20for%20people%20displaced%20in%20his%20district%20as%20well%20as%20those%20by%20other%20KLIP%20initiatives.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20alleged%20that%20people%20from%20different%20castes%20were%20paid%20different%20compensation%20rates%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20problems%20will%20be%20understood%20by%20the%20chief%20minister%20if%20we%20contest%20against%20him%20from%20his%20constituency.%20The%20issue%20will%20not%20be%20cleared%20unless%20the%20government%20leadership%20knows%20about%20it.%20I%20filed%20my%20nomination%20here%20to%20defeat%20KCR%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESugarcane%20farmers%20demand%20re-opening%20of%20once-prominent%20factory%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThree%20candidates%20from%20this%20seat%20%E2%80%93%20Baddam%20Srinivas%20Reddy%2C%20Mamidi%20Narayana%20Reddy%20and%20Navanandi%20Limbareddy%20%E2%80%93%20are%20sugarcane%20farmers%20who%20live%20in%20northern%20Telangana%E2%80%99s%20Jagityal%20(or%20Jagtial)%20district%2C%20a%20three-hour%20drive%20away%20from%20Gajwel.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20belong%20to%20a%20group%20of%20farmers%20who%20have%20long%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fstates%2Ftelangana%2F2023%2Fnov%2F03%2Fryots-demand-reopening-of-muthyampet-sugar-unit-2629583.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eprotested%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20the%20closing%20of%20the%20Nizam%20Sugar%20Factory%20in%20Nizamabad%20close%20to%20a%20decade%20ago%20(as%20well%20as%20some%20other%20sugar%20factories)%2C%20and%20demand%20their%20reopening.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBaddam%20Srinivas%20Reddy%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20economy%20of%20the%20area%20around%20the%20Nizam%20factory%20suffered%20a%20blow%20following%20the%20factory%E2%80%99s%20closure%2C%20as%20many%20people%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20benefited%20from%20the%20factory%E2%80%99s%20operations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20decided%20that%20our%20issue%20would%20come%20up%20for%20discussion%20only%20if%20we%20contested%20against%20the%20chief%20minister%20himself%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-bjp-isnt-a-frontrunner-but-could-it-be-a-spoilsport%5C%22%3ETelangana%20Polls%3A%20BJP%20Isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20Frontrunner%2C%20But%20Could%20it%20Be%20a%20Spoilsport%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20the%20Congress%20has%20said%20in%20their%20manifesto%20that%20they%20will%20open%20the%20sugar%20factories%20if%20they%20come%20to%20power%2C%20as%20has%20the%20BJP.%20It%20is%20very%20sad%20that%20the%20BRS%20has%20not%20even%20mentioned%20this%20issue%20in%20their%20manifesto%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srinivas%20Reddy%20continued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOthers%20in%20the%20fray%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOther%20independents%20in%20the%20fray%20from%20Gajwel%20said%20they%20wanted%20to%20highlight%20issues%20such%20as%20unemployment%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20official%20recognition%20for%20the%20Banjara%20(locally%20known%20as%20Lambadi)%20language%20and%20compensation%20for%20the%20kin%20of%20those%20who%20died%20for%20the%20Telangana%20statehood%20movement%20in%20the%20early%202010s.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDasari%20Haribabu%2C%20a%20PhD%20candidate%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Hyderabad%20and%20who%20is%20listed%20as%20residing%20in%20Gajwel%2C%20said%20he%20is%20contesting%20the%20election%20to%20sensitise%20people%20about%20unemployment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECriticising%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Feducation%2Fnews%2Ftspsc-group-1-prelims-exam-2023-cancelled-telangana-high-court-cancels-preliminary-exam%2Farticleshow%2F103884572.cms%5C%22%3Ecancellation%20of%20public%20service%20exams%20in%20the%20state%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cepitome%20of%20stupidity%E2%80%9D%2C%20Haribabu%20said%20they%20were%20especially%20painful%20as%20students%20had%20waited%20for%20a%20long%20time%20for%20exams%20to%20be%20notified.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20can%20any%20individual%20or%20educated%20person%20believe%20in%20and%20vote%20for%20%5BKCR%5D%3F%E2%80%9D%20Haribabu%20asked.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20acknowledged%20that%20he%20would%20get%20only%20a%20minor%20share%20of%20the%20votes%20in%20Gajwel%20but%20said%20his%20agenda%20was%20to%20%E2%80%9Csensitise%20the%20people%E2%80%9D%20and%20let%20the%20government%20know%20not%20to%20ignore%20the%20educated%20youth%2C%20and%20also%20recalled%20the%20narrative%20during%20the%20Telangana%20statehood%20movement%20that%20%E2%80%98Andhra%20people%E2%80%99%20taking%20a%20disproportionate%20number%20of%20jobs%20was%20resulting%20in%20unemployment%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHaribabu%20also%20said%20that%20a%20lack%20of%20good%20opportunities%20in%20rural%20areas%20was%20leading%20to%20young%20people%20not%20wanting%20to%20finish%20their%20studies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20see%20data%20about%20rural%20Telangana%2C%20you%20see%20that%20most%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20study%20beyond%20the%20tenth%20grade%20because%20there%20is%20no%20hope%2C%E2%80%9D%20Haribabu%20charged.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETelangana%20will%20go%20to%20the%20polls%20on%20Thursday%20(November%2030).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVotes%20for%20the%20elections%20in%20Telangana%20as%20well%20as%20those%20conducted%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Mizoram%20earlier%20this%20month%20will%20be%20counted%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWith%20additional%20reporting%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fvikram-mukka%2F%5C%22%3EVikram%20Mukka%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701086421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27153153%2FUntitled-design-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolit