.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EState%20education%20commissioner%20Amjad%20Kak%20told%20reporters%20in%20Itanagar%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20did%20scrutiny%20at%20the%20departmental%20level%2C%20issued%20show%20cause%20notices%20to%20all%2C%20and%20the%20termination%20orders%20were%20issued%20after%20the%20lapse%20of%20the%20notice%20period.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20controversial%20issue%20was%20first%20raised%20in%20March%202021%20by%20former%20Congress%20MP%20Ninong%20Ering.%20In%20response%2C%20though%20the%20chief%20minister%20Khandu%20had%20said%20strict%20action%20would%20be%20taken%20if%20the%20accusation%20was%20found%20to%20be%20true%2C%20but%20nothing%20much%20happened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20issue%20caught%20the%20public%20eye%20though.%20This%20past%20May%2C%20a%20student%20body%20accused%20the%20education%20department%20of%20appointing%2028%20primary%20school%20teachers%20without%20even%20issuing%20any%20advertisement%2C%20mandatory%20as%20per%20the%202018%20rules.%20The%20student%20body%20alleged%20that%20no%20interviews%20were%20even%20conducted%20before%20the%20teachers%20were%20appointed%20by%20the%20education%20department.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20led%20the%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20Youth%20Congress%20president%20Tarh%20Johny%20to%20file%20an%20FIR%20against%20the%20then%20elementary%20education%20director.%20The%20%3Cem%3EArunachal%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CUnder%20pressure%2C%20the%20state%20government%20gave%20approval%20to%20the%20vigilance%20department%E2%80%99s%20Special%20Investigation%20Cell%20(SIC)%20to%20probe%20into%20the%20cases%20in%20the%20education%20department%20in%20July%202023.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20past%20August%2C%20the%20SIC%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farunachaltimes.in%2Findex.php%2F2023%2F07%2F07%2Fseveral-illegal-appointments-in-education-dept-forces-goap-to-seek-sic-inquiry%2F%5C%22%3Eregistered%20a%20case%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20matter%20which%20led%20to%20a%20few%20arrests%20and%20the%20subsequent%20sacking%20of%20256%20such%20appointments.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20past%20November%2027%2C%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Farunachaltimes.in%2Findex.php%2F2023%2F11%2F25%2Fact-against-officials-involved-in-illegal-appointment%2F%5C%22%3Eeditorial%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20issue%20which%20has%20rocked%20the%20state%2C%20where%20elections%20will%20be%20held%20next%20year%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EArunachal%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20alleged%20that%20most%20of%20these%20appointees%20are%20linked%20to%20powerful%20people%2C%20including%20elected%20representatives.%20With%20the%20election%20nearing%2C%20many%20of%20them%20reportedly%20tried%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20political%20leadership%20to%20stop%20the%20department%20from%20initiating%20strong%20action%20against%20them.%E2%80%9D%20Lauding%20the%20education%20department%20for%20acting%20inspite%20of%20political%20pressure%2C%20the%20editorial%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20department%20still%20needs%20to%20act%20against%20the%20officials%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20scam.%20Now%20it%20needs%20to%20initiate%20strong%20action%20against%20those%20officials%20who%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20scam.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701084592000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27155123%2F404876061_927837082031569_6477364516950279346_n.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Farunachal-pradesh-sacks-256-people-education-department-fraud%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20development%20comes%20months%20after%20opposition%20parties%20accused%20the%20Pema%20Khandu%20government%20of%20appointing%20hundreds%20of%20employees%20%E2%80%9Cillegally%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20department.%22%2C%22au