20the%20Cold%20War-era%20Defense%20Production%20Act%20to%20boost%20investment%20in%20U.S.%20manufacturing%20of%20essential%20medicines%20and%20medical%20supplies.%20The%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%20will%20be%20authorized%20to%20enable%20these%20investments.%20The%20areas%20of%20investment%20also%20include%20medical%20countermeasures%20for%20chemical%2C%20biological%2C%20radiological%2C%20or%20nuclear%20attacks.%20Biden%20is%20addressing%20concerns%20about%20the%20U.S.%20economy%20and%20holding%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20White%20House%20Council%20on%20Supply%20Chain%20Resilience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-to-invoke-cold-war-era-law-to-boost-medical-supplies%2Farticleshow%2F105532997.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-to-invoke-cold-war-era-law-to-boost-medical-supplies%2Famp_articleshow%2F105532997.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fjoe-biden-to-invoke-cold-war-era-law-to-boost-medical-supplies%2Famp_articleshow%2F105532997.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Does%20Every%20BJP%20Election%20Campaign%20Centre%20Only%20On%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27145721%2F404088963_1118521242975440_6389008391481424915_n-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAs%202023%20comes%20to%20a%20close%2C%20five%20states%20will%20elect%20new%20legislative%20assemblies.%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20again%20the%20face%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20campaign%20in%20all%20these%20states%2C%20except%20Mizoram.%20This%20comes%20despite%20the%20expectation%20of%20political%20observers%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Telangana%20are%20not%20very%20bright%20and%20that%20Rajasthan%20will%20be%20a%20close%20contest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20again%20Modi%20vs%20the%20rest.%20No%20lessons%20have%20been%20learned%20from%20Karnataka%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20lost%20heavily%20earlier%20this%20year.%20There%2C%20too%2C%20Modi%20led%20the%20BJP%20campaign%20and%20made%20the%20election%20all%20about%20himself.%20Before%20the%20memory%20of%20that%20loss%20has%20even%20begun%20to%20fade%2C%20he%20has%20once%20again%20made%20these%20state%20elections%20all%20about%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20reason%20could%20be%20that%20since%202014%2C%20Modi%20has%20sought%20to%20project%20a%20regal%20aura%20%E2%80%93%20he%20sees%20himself%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98elected%20monarch%E2%80%99%20of%20India.%20And%20perhaps%20he%20wants%20his%20image%20in%20the%20public%20mind%20at%20all%20times.%20This%20is%20not%20for%20electoral%20reasons%20alone%3A%20he%20wants%20to%20make%20every%20discourse%20in%20India%20about%20himself.%20In%20fact%2C%20Indian%20citizens%20cannot%20escape%20his%20presence%20even%20in%20municipal%20elections%20%E2%80%93%20after%20all%2C%20people%20have%20seen%20him%20putting%20his%20reputation%20at%20stake%20even%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-hails-bjp-s-win-in-goa-municipal-elections-101616432760568.html%5C%22%3Elocal%20body%20elections%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20is%20to%20keep%20public%20discussion%20focused%20on%20himself.%20Modi%20alone%20is%20the%20agenda%20setter%20and%20subject%20of%20public%20discourse.%20All%20opposition%20parties%20are%20forced%20to%20respond%20to%20him%2C%20because%20he%20is%20the%20authoritative%20voice%20and%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20the%20party.%20Thus%20emerges%20the%20image%20of%20a%20single%20warrior%20battling%20scores%20of%20adversaries%2C%20which%20in%20itself%20is%20impressive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20reason%20for%20Modi%20keeping%20the%20electoral%20focus%20on%20himself%20could%20be%20to%20project%20himself%20as%20the%20personification%20of%20%E2%80%98development%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ci%3EVikas%20Purush%3C%2Fi%3E%20or%20%E2%80%98Development%20Man%E2%80%99.%20And%20yet%20he%20seems%20to%20give%20himself%20the%20freedom%2C%20whenever%20needed%2C%20to%20run%20an%20election%20campaign%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fwith-modis-blessing-bjps-communal-agenda-gets-a-boost-in-coastal-karnataka%5C%22%3Edivides%20the%20electorate%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20communal%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20can%20be%20crass%20and%20anti-Muslim%20in%20his%20election%20speeches%2C%20but%20his%20position%20as%20prime%20minister%20prevents%20public%20criticism.%20In%20the%20recently%20held%20elections%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20he%20even%20raised%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmangaluru%2Fpm-modi-raises-pitch-against-congress-proposal-to-ban-bajrang-dal%2Farticleshow%2F99979517.cms%5C%22%3Eslogan%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Bajrang%20Dal%2C%20one%20of%20the%20many%20militant%20outfits%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20the%20fount%20of%20Hindu%20nationalist%20politics.%20There%20was%20no%20public%20uproar.%20Even%20a%20cursory%20look%20at%20his%20election%20speeches%20would%20reveal%20that%20he%20has%20been%20doing%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F918630%2Fthe-daily-fix-goodbye-vikas-modi-and-the-bjp-have-decided-to-run-an-explicitly-communal-campaign%5C%22%3Econsistently%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20largely%20uncritical%20media%20appears%20to%20give%20him%20a%20free%20pass%20for%20his%20divisive%20electioneering%2C%20perhaps%20dismissing%20his%20communal%20rhetoric%20as%20electoral%20compulsion.%20When%20Modi%20is%20engaged%20in%20an%20electoral%20battle%2C%20it%20almost%20appears%20as%20if%20the%20media%20joins%20forces%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20always%20a%20winning%20formula%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20projection%20of%20Modi%20as%20the%20sole%20face%20of%20the%20BJP%20does%20not%20always%20lead%20to%20electoral%20victories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20was%202015.%20Delhi%20was%20going%20to%20the%20polls%20to%20elect%20the%20legislative%20assembly.%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20been%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%20for%20barely%20nine%20months%20and%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%98Modi%20wave%E2%80%99%20was%20in%20full%20flow.%20Delhi%20is%20not%20even%20a%20full%20state%2C%20yet%20Modi%2C%20the%20supreme%20leader%20of%20the%20ruling%20BJP%2C%20decided%20to%20make%20it%20his%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20media%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Fassembly-elections-2015%2Fdelhi%2Fstory%2Fdelhi-election-results-kejriwal-aap-sweeps-delhi-bjp-modi-239638-2015-02-10%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20had%20made%20Delhi%20a%20high-stakes%20battle%20with%20a%20massive%20ad%20blitzkrieg%20asking%20for%20votes%20in%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20name.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20led%20an%20aggressive%20campaign%20telling%20the%20electorate%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20a%20BJP%20government%20in%20Delhi%2C%20then%20those%20here%20will%20be%20afraid%20of%20Modi%20and%20the%20central%20government.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20BJP%20lost%20badly.%20Their%20defeat%20under%20Modi%20was%20massive%2C%20with%20the%20party%20slumping%20to%20just%20three%20seats%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Legislative%20Assembly%2C%20from%20its%20earlier%20tally%20of%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20rushed%20to%20clarify%20that%20it%20was%20merely%20a%20state%20election%20fought%20on%20local%20issues%20and%20should%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20referendum%20on%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20after%20the%20Delhi%20debacle%2C%20Modi%20led%20another%20election%20campaign%20%E2%80%93%20this%20time%20in%20Bihar%2C%20which%20was%20going%20to%20the%20polls.%20The%20BJP%20lost%20again.%20Reuters%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Findia-bihar-election-result-jdu-bjp-modi-idUSKCN0SX04P20151108%2F%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20suffered%20a%20heavy%20defeat%20on%20Sunday%20in%20an%20election%20in%20Bihar%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20third%20most-populous%20state%2C%20signalling%20the%20waning%20power%20of%20a%20leader%20who%20until%20recently%20had%20an%20unrivalled%20reputation%20as%20a%20vote%20winner.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20myth%20of%20Modi%20as%20an%20unbeatable%20political%20leader%20has%20been%20broken%20again%20and%20again%20in%20the%20state%20legislative%20assembly%20elections.%20Be%20it%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20or%20the%20northeastern%20states%20like%20Manipur%20and%20Meghalaya%2C%20the%20BJP%20lost%20despite%20Modi%20being%20its%20chief%20campaigner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Modi%20did%20after%20losing%20the%20elections%20was%20to%20break%20the%20opposition%20parties%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fcongress-has-lost-six-governments-to-bjp-since-pm-narendra-modi-assumed-power-in-2014-954411.html%5C%22%3Edefections%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20essentially%20%E2%80%98buying%20up%E2%80%99%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20legislators%20to%20topple%20the%20elected%20government.%20He%20thus%20snatched%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20mandate%20in%20Manipur%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Karnataka%20from%20the%20Congress%20party%20even%20after%20losing%20the%20elections.%20These%20developments%20were%20presented%20as%20master%20strokes%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Leader%20who%20could%20turn%20electoral%20defeats%20into%20victories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20significant%20that%20in%20the%20current%20elections%20in%20five%20states%2C%20he%20has%20chosen%20not%20to%20address%20even%20a%20single%20meeting%20in%20Mizoram%20as%20the%20decimation%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state%20seems%20certain%20%E2%80%93%20in%20part%20because%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20unpopularity%20among%20the%20Mizos.%20After%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20insensitive%20handling%20of%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20neighbouring%20Manipur%2C%20tribal%20communities%20displaced%20by%20the%20violence%20took%20shelter%20in%20Mizoram%20because%20of%20their%20close%20ethnic%20connections%20with%20the%20people%20of%20the%20state.%20Modi%20avoided%20going%20to%20Mizoram%20to%20campaign%2C%20clearly%20not%20wanting%20his%20name%20associated%20with%20defeat.%20In%20fact%2C%20even%20the%20Mizoram%20chief%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20an%20ally%20of%20the%20BJP%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ffive-reasons-mizoram-cm-zoramthanga-shun-modi-election%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20want%20to%20share%20a%20stage%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20essentially%20symbolised%20by%20Modi.%20No%20other%20leaders%20in%20the%20party%20matter.%20This%20is%20what%20gives%20a%20sense%20of%20inevitability%20about%20him.%20Even%20while%20he%20keeps%20doing%20badly%20in%20the%20state%20polls%2C%20the%20media%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia-today-insight%2Fstory%2Fhow-narendra-modi-looks-all-set-to-return-in-2024-2431344-2023-09-05%23%5C%22%3Ekeeps%20up%20the%20narrative%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20remains%20the%20people%E2%80%99s%20only%20choice%20for%20prime%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EApoorvanand%20teaches%20at%20Delhi%20University.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701079230000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27145721%2F404088963_1118521242975440_6389008391481424915_n-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-election-campaign-centre-prime-minister-modi%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Narendra%20Modi%20is%20not%20always%20a%20winning%20formula%20for%20the%20BJP.%20But%20perhaps%20he%20wants%20his%20image%20in%20the%20public%20mind%20at%20all%20times.%20This%20is%20not%20for%20electoral%20reasons%20alone%3A%20he%20wants%20to%20make%20every%20discourse%20in%20India%20about%20himself.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-election-campaign-centre-prime-minister-modi%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine's%20Avdiivka%20empties%20in%20face%20of%20Russian%20assaults%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701079119000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105532998%2Cimgsize-676305.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraines-avdiivka-empties-in-face-of-russian-assaults%2Farticleshow%2F105532878.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105532878.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EA%20Ukrainian%20soldier%20named%20Taxist%20drives%20an%20armoured%20Humvee%20through%20Avdiivka%2C%20a%20town%20in%20Ukraine's%20eastern%20region%20of%20Donetsk.%20Avdiivka%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20ongoing%20war%20between%20Ukrainian%20and%20Russian%20forces.%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20navigate%20the%20roads%20cautiously%20to%20avoid%20being%20targeted%20by%20Russian%20artillery%20or%20drones.%20Despite%20the%20dangers%2C%20some%20residents%2C%20like%20Oksana%20and%20retiree%20Oleksandre%20Makarov%2C%20choose%20to%20stay%20in%20Avdiivka%20due%20to%20their%20attachment%20to%20the%20town%20and%20lack%20of%20resources%20to%20start%20anew.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraines-avdiivka-empties-in-face-of-russian-assaults%2Farticleshow%2F105532878.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraines-avdiivka-empties-in-face-of-russian-assaults%2Famp_articleshow%2F105532878.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraines-avdiivka-empties-in-face-of-russian-assaults%2Famp_articleshow%2F105532878.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Can%20the%20Resurgent%20Congress%20Wrest%20Telangana%20from%20the%20BRS%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EBarely%20six%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20Telangana%20political%20landscape%20looked%20vastly%20different%20from%20what%20it%20is%20today.%20The%20upcoming%20assembly%20election%2C%20it%20was%20perceived%20then%2C%20would%20be%20a%20straight%20fight%20between%20the%20incumbent%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20and%20an%20aggressive%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20Congress%2C%20the%20grand%20old%20party%2C%20was%20written%20off.%20Crestfallen%20party%20leaders%20and%20cadres%20were%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20alternative%20options%20for%20their%20political%20survival.%20Today%2C%20however%2C%20anyone%20in%20Telangana%20would%20agree%20(barring%20the%20ruling%20BRS)%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20stock%20has%20gone%20up%20by%20several%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20339px)%2085vw%2C%20339px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22339%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22280%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20contention%20about%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20ascendancy%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20question%2C%20however%2C%20is%20whether%20it%20has%20grown%20to%20the%20extent%20where%20it%20can%20wrest%20power.%20Even%20as%20we%20inch%20closer%20to%20the%20polling%20date%20(November%2030)%2C%20pollsters%20are%20still%20not%20able%20to%20call%20the%20election.%20There%20seems%20to%20be%20no%20discernible%20wave%20for%20or%20against%20the%20BRS%2C%20and%20likewise%20the%20Congress.%20This%20is%20evidenced%20by%20numerous%20surveys%2C%20each%20one%20of%20them%20projecting%20vastly%20different%20numbers%20for%20the%20two%20main%20contenders%2C%20the%20BRS%20and%20the%20Congress.%20Some%20of%20them%20even%20don%E2%80%99t%20rule%20out%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20hung%20assembly%2C%20with%20some%20giving%20the%20BRS%20a%20slight%20edge%20and%20others%20for%20the%20Congress.%20One%20thing%20common%20in%20these%20surveys%20is%20the%20clear%20resurgence%20of%20the%20Congress%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20factors%20could%20have%20contributed%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20upturn%3A%20Perceived%20anti-incumbency%20at%20the%20constituency%20level%20against%20BRS%20MLAs%3B%20energy%20infused%20by%20the%20Karnataka%20victory%20in%20the%20party%20leaders%20and%20cadres%3B%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20decline%20following%20the%20removal%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fare-cracks-appearing-in-bjps-telangana-unit-after-the-karnataka-debacle%5C%22%3EBandi%20Sanjay%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20Telangana%20unit%20chief%3B%20and%20the%20perception%20that%20the%20BRS%20and%20All%20India%20Majlis-e-Ittehadul%20Muslimeen%20(AIMIM)%20are%20in%20cahoots%20with%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMessaging%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20sole%20credit%20for%20themselves%20in%20the%20establishment%20of%20Telangana%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BRS%20describe%20themselves%20as%20%3Cem%3Eichchina%3C%2Fem%3E%20party%20(the%20party%20that%20granted%20the%20statehood)%20and%20%3Cem%3Etechchina%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eparty%20(the%20party%20that%20achieved%20statehood%20through%20agitation)%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20been%20training%20its%20guns%20on%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekhar%20Rao%20and%20his%20family%2C%20accusing%20them%20of%20turning%20Telangana%20into%20their%20%E2%80%9Cfiefdom%E2%80%9D%2C%20much%20like%20the%20feudal%20lords%20(Doras)%20of%20the%20yore.%20The%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20messaging%20appears%20to%20have%20found%20some%20takers%2C%20given%20the%20widespread%20allegations%20against%20KCR%20that%20he%20is%20inaccessible%20(which%20earned%20him%20the%20moniker%20of%20%E2%80%9Cfarmhouse%20CM%E2%80%9D)%20and%20that%20power%20is%20concentrated%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204101%2Fkcr-ktr.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204101%2Fkcr-ktr.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204101%2Fkcr-ktr-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F01%2F04204101%2Fkcr-ktr-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-425083%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EK.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20with%20his%20son%20K.T.%20Rama%20Rao.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20has%20also%20foregrounded%20alleged%20repression%20under%20KCR%2C%20that%20he%20had%20engineered%20defections%20of%20opposition%20MLAs%20to%20the%20ruling%20party%20to%20curb%20political%20dissent%20as%20well%20as%20numerous%20instances%20of%20the%20arrest%20of%20civil%20society%20members%20and%20closure%20of%20civil%20society%20spaces.%20The%20widespread%20allegations%20of%20corruption%20against%20KCR%20and%20his%20family%20members%2C%20including%20in%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20much-publicised%20Kaleshwaram%20Project%2C%20have%20also%20provided%20fodder%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20campaign%2C%20which%20has%20been%20egging%20on%20the%20people%20to%20join%20hands%20in%20%E2%80%9Canother%20struggle%E2%80%9D%20to%20%E2%80%9Cliberate%E2%80%9D%20Telangana%20from%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EDorala%20Palana%3C%2Fem%3E%20(rule%20by%20Doras)%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-brs-anti-incumbency-congress%5C%22%3ETelangana%20Polls%3A%20Can%20BRS%20Fend%20Off%20Anti-Incumbency%20Sentiment%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManifesto%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20lines%20of%20its%20Karnataka%20manifesto%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20announced%20six%20%E2%80%98guarantees%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20voters%20of%20Telangana.%20The%20manifesto%2C%20which%20is%20high%20on%20welfare%20and%20covers%20various%20sections%20of%20society%2C%20could%20work%20in%20its%20favour.%20The%20BRS%2C%20aware%20of%20the%20damage%20potential%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20manifesto%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Ftelangana%2Fbrs-attempts-to-trump-congress-manifesto-with-few-more-novel-sops%2Farticle67424024.ece%5C%22%3Esought%20to%20outshine%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20its%20own%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20Mahalaxmi%20guarantee%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20announced%20Rs%202%2C500%20per%20month%20to%20eligible%20women.%20The%20BRS%2C%20for%20its%20part%2C%20promises%20Rs%203%2C000%20as%20a%20monthly%20honorarium.%20While%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20provide%20an%20LPG%20cylinder%20at%20Rs%20500%2C%20the%20BRS%20has%20said%20it%20will%20offer%20the%20same%20at%20Rs%20400.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20to%20increase%20investment%20support%20given%20to%20farmers%20(under%20the%20existing%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20of%20the%20BRS%20government)%20from%20Rs%2010%2C000%20to%20Rs%2015%2C000%20per%20acre%20per%20year.%20The%20Congress%20has%20also%20gone%20a%20step%20further%20by%20promising%20it%20to%20tenant%20farmers%20as%20well%2C%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20benefit%20under%20the%20Rythu%20Bandhu%20scheme.%20The%20BRS%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20has%20promised%20to%20make%20it%20Rs%2016%2C000%20per%20acre%20per%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20its%20Cheyutha%20scheme%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20Rs%204%2C000%20per%20month%20to%20old-age%20pension%20beneficiaries.%20The%20BRS%20has%20assured%20them%20that%20it%20would%20raise%20the%20amount%20from%20existing%20Rs%202%2C000%20to%20Rs%205%2C000%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20is%20largely%20banking%20on%20the%20youth%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fpolitical-pulse%2Ftelanganas-exam-hub-trials-and-tribulations-of-job-aspirants-9033684%2F%5C%22%3Egovernment%20job%20aspirants%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20are%20angry%20with%20the%20BRS%20government.%20Even%20by%20its%20own%20admission%2C%20the%20BRS%20government%20has%20failed%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftelangana%2Fthe-unemployment-problem-in-telangana-what-jobs-data-tells-us%5C%22%3Eunemployed%20youth%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20state%2C%20by%20not%20being%20able%20to%20fill%20vacancies%20and%20conduct%20recruitment%20exams%20without%20any%20irregularities.%20The%20youth%20seems%20clearly%20not%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20BRS%2C%20which%20could%20help%20shore%20up%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20prospects.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20gone%20even%20a%20step%20further%20by%20announcing%20a%20job%20calendar%2C%20confident%20of%20forming%20the%20next%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20other%20segments%20who%20are%20disillusioned%20by%20the%20BRS%20government%20are%20government%20employees%20who%20have%20been%20waiting%20for%20long%20for%20interim%20relief%2C%20restoration%20of%20the%20Old%20Pension%20Scheme%2C%20and%20Pay%20Revision%20Commission%20(PRC)%2C%20among%20other%20issues.%20A%20large%20number%20of%20those%20who%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fpolitics%2F260923%2Fdalit-bc-bandhu-gruha-lakshmi-fear-brs-mlas.html%5C%22%3Eleft%20out%20of%20the%20BRS%20government%20schemes%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Dalit%20Bandhu%20and%20double-bedroom%20housing%20could%20potentially%20vote%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20Congress.%20Both%20Muslim%20and%20Christian%20minorities%20could%20also%20rally%20behind%20the%20Congress%20due%20to%20its%20effective%20messaging%20that%20the%20BRS%20and%20BJP%20are%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20same%20coin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20perception%20of%20the%20BJP%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20BRS%20has%20lowered%20significantly%20since%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20the%20party%20could%20play%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-bjp-isnt-a-frontrunner-but-could-it-be-a-spoilsport%5C%22%3Espoilsport%20for%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20splitting%20the%20anti-incumbency%20votes%20in%20several%20constituencies.%20The%20Congress%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20face%20a%20stiff%20fight%20for%20anti-BRS%20votes%20in%20about%2020%20seats%2C%20including%20in%20Korutla%2C%20LB%20Nagar%2C%20Bodhan%2C%20Kamareddy%2C%20Nirmal%2C%20Maheshwaram%2C%20and%20in%20a%20few%20handful%20of%20seats%20of%20the%20Greater%20Hyderabad%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(GHMC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Congress%2C%20it%20is%20still%20an%20uphill%20task%20despite%20the%20positive%20perception%20it%20has%20built%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months%20given%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20role%20as%20well%20as%20the%20BRS%E2%80%99s%20public%20relations%20overdrive%20and%20poll%20management.%20A%20senior%20party%20leader%20remarked%20that%20the%20Congress%20party%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20form%20the%20next%20government%20in%20the%20state%20even%20if%20it%20wins%20one%20seat%20less%20than%2060%20in%20the%20119-member%20assembly%20due%20to%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20BRS%20and%20BJP%20coming%20together.%20Can%20the%20Congress%20pull%20off%20a%20handsome%20victory%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701077347000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27132111%2FThe-Wire-91.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fresurgent-congress-telangana-brs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20as%20we%20inch%20closer%20to%20the%20polling%20date%20(November%2030)%2C%20pollsters%20are%20still%20not%20able%20to%20call%20the%20election%20given%20that%20there%20seems%20to%20be%20no%20discernible%20wave%20for%20or%20against%20the%20BRS%2C%20and%20likewise%20the%20Congress.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fresurgent-congress-telangana-brs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20families%20of%20MH370%20crash%20victims%20are%20calling%20for%20new%20search%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701077295000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105539042%2Cimgsize-1727780.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fwhat-happened-to-our-loved-ones-why-families-of-mh370-crash-victims-are-calling-for-a-new-search%2Farticleshow%2F105531522.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Relatives%20of%20Chinese%20passengers%20lost%20in%20the%20MH370%20tragedy%20called%20for%