news%2Fdid-railways-really-reduce-sleeper-coaches-in-trains-false-says-ashwini-vaishnaw-101700154390576.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cfact%20checking%E2%80%9D%20claims%20of%20overcrowding%20in%20trains%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20around%20the%20Chhath%20Puja%20festival.%20As%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fdiwali-train-rush-indian-railways-stampede-social-media-crowd-2462022-2023-11-12%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Evisuals%20of%20jam-packed%20railway%20platforms%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20went%20viral%2C%20the%20Railways%20said%2C%20contrary%20to%20claims%2C%20that%20there%20had%20been%20no%20reduction%20in%20General%20and%20Sleeper%20coaches%20in%20either%20special%20trains%20launched%20during%20the%20festive%20seasons%20or%20in%20long-distance%20express%20trains.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAn%20official%20circular%20dated%20October%2014%2C%20detailing%20a%20revised%20schedule%20for%20long-distance%20express%20trains%2C%20was%20seen%20circulating%20on%20social%20media%20too.%20As%20per%20that%20circular%2C%20there%20are%20six%20to%20seven%20Sleeper%20coaches%20and%20four%20General%20or%20unreserved%20coaches%20in%20every%2022-rake%20train.%20The%20implication%20is%20that%20this%20number%20has%20remained%20constant%20for%20the%20past%20three%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20truth%2C%20however%2C%20is%20a%20little%20different.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20figures%20have%20shown%20that%20the%20production%20of%20General%20and%20Sleeper%20coaches%20is%20being%20drastically%20reduced%20in%20favour%20of%20air-conditioned%20ones.%20Significantly%2C%20figures%20have%20confirmed%20that%20this%20trend%20will%20continue%20into%20the%20next%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParsing%20these%20figures%20reveals%20a%20double%20whammy%20for%20economy%20passengers.%20For%20now%2C%20it%20appears%20that%20passengers%20will%20have%20to%20continue%20travelling%20in%20jam-packed%20compartments%20for%20the%20next%20two%20years%20or%20more%2C%20after%20which%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20shell%20out%20higher%20fares%20if%20they%20wish%20to%20travel%20by%20train.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERailways%20officials%20not%20wishing%20to%20be%20identified%20have%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20announcement%20that%20there%20are%20adequate%20General%20and%20Sleeper%20coaches%20to%20go%20around%20is%20not%20the%20truth.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20rail%20coach%20factories%20(RCFs)%20across%20the%20country%20go%20by%20the%20schedule%20given%20to%20them%20for%20the%20manufacture%20of%20coaches.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20they%20are%20following%20the%20schedule%20issued%20in%20June%20last%20year%20when%20the%20production%20of%20General%20and%20Sleeper%20coaches%20was%20revised%20downwards%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20railway%20official%20told%20this%20correspondent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20official%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20are%20to%20go%20back%20to%20making%20these%20coaches%20in%20adequate%20capacity%2C%20then%20the%20RCFs%20will%20have%20to%20stop%20all%20production%20of%20the%20AC%20coaches%20to%20meet%20this%20revised%20schedule%20issued%20last%20month.%20So%20at%20least%20for%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20no%20relief%20for%20passengers%20wishing%20to%20travel%20only%20in%20General%20and%20Sleeper%20classes.%20Therefore%2C%20such%20trains%20are%20going%20to%20be%20as%20crowded%20as%20they%20are%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20production%20schedule%20for%202023-24%20and%202024-25%20seen%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20indicates%20that%201%2C142%20General%20and%20Sleeper%20coaches%20will%20be%20manufactured%20by%20RCFs.%20In%20contrast%2C%203%2C044%20air-conditioned%20coaches%20will%20be%20produced%20during%20this%20time%20period.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20be%20precise%2C%20the%20production%20of%20General%20coaches%2C%20now%20renamed%20%E2%80%98Deen%20Dayalu%E2%80%99%20after%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20icon%2C%20Deen%20Dayal%20Upadhyaya%2C%20will%20be%20438%20for%202023-24%20and%202024-25.%20That%20of%20Sleeper%20coaches%2C%20will%20be%20704.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20air-conditioned%20coaches%2C%20the%20number%20of%20AC%203-tier%20economy%20coaches%20that%20will%20be%20manufactured%20by%20RCFs%20will%20be%202%2C253%2C%20clearly%20more%20than%20the%20General%20and%20Sleeper%20class%20coaches.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENotably%2C%20it%20is%20the%20economy%20coaches%20have%20come%20in%20for%20increased%20criticism%20over%20space%20constraints%20following%20the%20introduction%20of%20extra%20berths%2C%20but%20that%20has%20not%20stopped%20the%20railway%20board%20from%20going%20full%20steam%20ahead.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBesides%20economy%2C%20the%20production%20of%20AC%203-tier%20coaches%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20402%20and%20that%20of%20AC%202-tier%20is%20389.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98A%20different%20colour%20scheme%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20we%20start%20manufacturing%20more%20General%20and%20Sleeper%20coaches%2C%20these%20will%20be%20prioritised%20for%20the%20new%20Vande%20Sadharan%20trains%20that%20are%20undergoing%20trial%20runs%20at%20the%20moment.%20These%20trains%20will%20have%20the%20standard%2022%20coaches%2C%20of%20which%2012%20will%20be%20sleeper%20and%20eight%20general%20compartments%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20an%20official%20at%20the%20Rail%20Coach%20Factory%2C%20Kapurthala.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVande%20Sadharan%20or%20Amrit%20Bharat%20trains%20are%20in%20contrast%20to%20their%20more%20elite%20and%20expensive%20brethren%2C%20the%20Vande%20Bharat.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CVande%20Sadharan%20are%20nothing%20but%20ordinary%20long-distance%20express%20trains%20whose%20design%20has%20been%20tweaked%20somewhat%2C%20and%20they%20come%20in%20a%20different%20colour%20scheme.%20The%20train%20is%20in%20answer%20to%20the%20criticism%20the%20government%20is%20facing%20about%20catering%20to%20only%20the%20rich%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sarabjeet%20Singh%2C%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Rail%20Coach%20Factory%2C%20Kapurthala%20Employees%20Union%2C%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20maintained%20a%20studied%20silence%20over%20the%20criticism%20regarding%20Vande%20Bharat%20and%20other%20premium%20trains%20and%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20policy%20of%20turning%20the%20railways%20into%20a%20for-profit%20organisation%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20public%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Knee-jerk%20reactions%2C%20tinkerings%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20are%20also%20questions%20being%20raised%20at%20various%20rail%20coach%20factories%20%E2%80%93%20that%20produce%20a%20bulk%20of%20the%20railway%20stock%20%E2%80%93%20about%20the%20flip-flopping%20attitude%20of%20the%20government%20in%20its%20production%20of%20AC%20and%20non-AC%20coaches.%20Some%20called%20the%20government%20suddenly%20starting%20the%20production%20of%20non-AC%20coaches%20a%20knee-jerk%20reaction%20to%20the%20criticism.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20also%20been%20tinkering%20with%20production%20schedules%20and%20revising%20them%20frequently.%20A%20comparison%20of%20the%20last%20three%20schedules%20issued%20by%20the%20department%20of%20coaching%20throws%20up%20conflicting%20plans.%20The%20October%202023%20schedule%20for%20a%2022-coach%20rake%20has%20between%20six%20and%20seven%20sleeper%20coaches%20and%20four%20general%20compartments.%20There%20are%20six%20AC%203-tier%20and%20AC%203-tier%20economy%20coaches%20and%20two%20AC%202%20tier%20coaches%20respectively.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20of%20October%202020%2C%20the%20number%20of%20Sleeper%20coaches%20in%20a%2022-rake%20train%20was%20seven.%20AC%203-tier%20and%20AC%202-tier%20coaches%20were%20six%20and%20two%20respectively%2C%20and%20the%20number%20of%20unreserved%20compartments%20was%20four.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20June%202022%2C%20the%20number%20of%20sleeper%20coaches%20had%20come%20down%20to%20two%20while%20AC%203-tier%20and%20economy%20AC%20coaches%20had%20gone%20up%20to%2010.%20The%20number%20of%20AC%202-tier%20coaches%20had%20doubled%20to%20four.%20There%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20General%20compartments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20Railway%20Board%20had%20a%20change%20of%20heart%20in%20October%20this%20year%20and%20increased%20the%20number%20of%20unreserved%20compartments%2C%20the%20question%20that%20is%20being%20asked%20is%20whether%20this%20is%20implementable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20policy%20decision%20is%20not%20at%20all%20viable%20and%20the%20revised%20schedule%20is%20more%20to%20fob%20off%20criticism%20of%20overcrowding%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20multiple%20Railway%20officials.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20one%20official%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20railways%20are%20hopeful%20that%20the%20shortage%20will%20be%20met.%20The%20minister%20has%20already%20said%20that%20infrastructure%20is%20being%20improved%20and%20more%20tracks%20will%20be%20laid%2C%20that%20the%20speed%20of%20trains%20will%20be%20increased%20and%20that%20at%20least%203%2C000%20new%20trains%20will%20be%20manufactured%20to%20reduce%20the%20problem%20of%20waitlisted%20passengers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Railway%20Board%20had%20in%202020%20decided%20to%20upgrade%20non-AC%20coaches%20to%20AC%20ones%20for%20all%20trains%20running%20at%20130%20km%20per%20hour.%20This%20would%20cut%20out%20dust%20and%20noise%2C%20and%20improve%20speed%2C%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701075629000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F27141653%2F6703159841_a87e2a4aae_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-the-railways-figures-spell-doom-for-economy-passengers%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20appears%20that%20Indians%20will%20have%20to%20continue%20travelling%20in%20jam-packed%20General%20and%20Sleeper%20compartments%20for%20the%20next%20two%20years%20or%20more%2C%20after%20which%2C%20they%20will%20have%20to%20shell%20out%20higher%20fares%20if%20they%20wish%20to%20travel%20by%20train.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-the-railways-figures-spell-doom-for-economy-passengers%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gangs%2C%20extortion%20in%20Bangladesh%20camps%20driving%20Rohingya%20sea%20exodus%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701074633000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105530928%2Cimgsize-120524.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fgangs-extortion-in-bangladesh-camps-driving-rohingya-sea-exodus%2Farticleshow%2F105530865.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F105530865.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EHaving%20first%20fled%20state-backed%20persecution%20in%20Myanmar%20--%20including%20a%202017%20crackdown%20that%20is%20subject%20to%20a%20UN%20genocide%20probe%20--%20the%20refugees%20now%20find%20themselves%20pushed%20to%20undertake%20weeks-long%20journeys%20of%20more%20than%201%2C800%20kilometres%20(1%2C120%20miles)%20on%20packed%2C%20rickety%20boats.%20Indonesia%20is%20not%20a%20signatory%20to%20the%20UN%20Refugee%20Convention%20and%20says%20it%20is%20not%20compelled%20to%20take%20in%20refugees%20from%20Myanmar%2C%20but%20neighbouring%20countries%20have%20shut%20their%20doors%2C%20meaning%20they%20have%20almost%20no%20other%20options.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fgangs-extortion-in-bangladesh-camps-driving-rohingya-sea-exodus%2Farticleshow%2F105530865.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fgangs-extortion-in-bangladesh-camps-driving-rohingya-sea-exodus%2Famp_articleshow%2F105530865.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fsouth-asia%2Fgangs-extortion-in-bangladesh-camps-driving-rohingya-sea-exodus%2Famp_articleshow%2F105530865.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mizoram%3A%20Churches%20Pray%20for%20Change%20in%20Counting%20Date%20for%20Assembly%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F14184445%2Fpexels-m-15226359.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20This%20Sunday%2C%20churches%20across%20Christian-majority%20Mizoram%20prayed%20for%20an%20unusual%20reason.%20They%20sought%20%E2%80%98divine%20intervention%E2%80%99%20to%20help%20reschedule%20the%20December%203%20date%20for%20the%20counting%20of%20votes%20polled%20in%20the%20recently-held%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20Northeastern%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDecember%203%20is%20a%20Sunday%2C%20the%20day%20of%20worship%20for%20Christians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThough%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20usually%20takes%20special%20days%20into%20consideration%20while%20picking%20election%20dates%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmizoram-election-commission-counting-day-sunday-christians%5C%22%3Ethe%20plea%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20several%20civil%20society%20groups%2C%20political%20parties%20and%20the%20Church%20to%20postpone%20the%20counting%20day%20for%20Mizoram%20by%20a%20day%20or%20two%20has%20not%20been%20heeded.%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20the%20ECI%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Felection-commission-weddings-rajasthan-date%5C%22%3Echanged%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20date%20of%20polling%20from%20November%2023%20to%20November%2025%20after%20receiving%20representations%20that%20%E2%80%9Clarge%20scale%20wedding%E2%80%9D%20ceremonies%20were%20scheduled%20on%20the%20earlier%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20the%20Mizoram%20Kohhran%20Hruaitute%20Committee%20(MKHC)%2C%20a%20conglomerate%20of%2015%20major%20churches%20of%20the%20state%2C%20urged%20all%20churches%20this%20past%20Saturday%20(November%2025)%20to%20organise%20prayers%20during%20the%20Sunday%20church%20service%20to%20seek%20%E2%80%9Chelp%20from%20God%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20change%20in%20the%20counting%20date.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMizoram%20Presbyterian%20Church%2C%20the%20largest%20denomination%20in%20the%20state%2C%20also%20separately%20urged%20its%20members%20to%20hold%20prayers%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20date%20of%20counting%20is%20changed%2C%20said%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.themizorampost.net%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EMizoram%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20five-member%20delegation%20of%20the%20NGO%20Coordination%20Committee%20(NGOCC)%2C%20an%20Aizawl-based%20umbrella%20body%20of%20NGOs%20and%20student%20organisations%2C%20has%20been%20staying%20put%20in%20New%20Delhi%20since%20the%20past%20week%20to%20seek%20an%20appointment%20with%20the%20chief%20election%20commissioner%20(CEC)%20on%20the%20matter.%20The%20delegation%20has%20come%20to%20the%20national%20Capital%20after%20pleas%20by%20civil%20society%20groups%20and%20political%20parties%20to%20the%20State%20Election%20Commission%20(SEC)%20went%20unheard.%20Those%20pleas%20were%20made%20as%20soon%20as%20the%20CEC%20in%20New%20Delhi%20had%20announced%20the%20election%20schedule%20in%20the%20state%20along%20with%20December%203%20as%20the%20common%20date%20for%20counting%20of%20votes%20in%20all%20the%20five%20poll-bound%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENews%20reports%20said%20the%20CEC%E2%80%99s%20office%20has%20given%20time%20to%20the%20delegation%20on%20November%2028.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20SEC%20has%20made%20all%20arrangements%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20counting%20on%20December%203%20as%20scheduled.%20A%20%3Cem%3EMizoram%20Post%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20quoting%20additional%20chief%20election%20officer%20H.%20Lianzela%20said%20more%20than%204%2C000%20counting%20personnel%20would%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20counting%20exercise%20which%20was%20to%20begin%20at%208%20am.%20In%20all%2C%2013%20counting%20centres%20would%20be%20set%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20November%2029%2C%20a%20full%20dress%20rehearsal%20of%20the%20counting%20exercise%20would%20be%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20SEC%20for%20smooth%20conduct%20on%20the%20designated%20day%2C%20state%20chief%20election%20officer%20Madhup%20Vyas%20told%20reporters%20in%20Aizwal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1701073505000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F02%2F14184445%2Fpexels-m-15226359.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Freligion%2Fmizoram-churches-pray-change-counting-date-assembly-polls%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20counting%20is%20scheduled%20on%20December%203%2C%20a%20Sunday%20and%20the%20day%20of%20worship%20for%20Christians.%20Several%20civi